//api.change.org/u/36407362"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T19:30:47Z","content":"I shop for 4-h raised meat whenever possible at our co-op because I don't like the meat of tortured animals It doesn't go down well","like_count":0,"author_name":"Abelone Edwards","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6610211"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T20:54:20Z","content":"Animals deserve dignity and respect in any circumstance including their inevitable demise.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erika Zanatta Maurano","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27501316"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T21:06:16Z","content":"To subject any living creature to a life confined to a space as small as these cages is just an outright disgrace and horrible reflection of us as Canadians.  We strive to appear so righteous and then allow this to be acceptable in our own country, it is not right, especially considering it is all about the almighty dollar, shame on the companies and farms that continue to allow this in their facilities.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Edward Eigelshoven","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26900890"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T03:11:56Z","content":"Because I have always had a soft spot in my heart for animals and to treat them so poorly reflects badly on the whole human race. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Lowe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7554833"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:11:42Z","content":"To mistreat the helpless is to become lower than the dust.  Humans must become better than this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Morgen Aiken","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11876309"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T15:22:52Z","content":"Animals have feelings and torture hurts! This disreguard for these animals well being and feelings must stop. how can we call ourselves the more intelligent species when we still continue to turn our heads away from this abuse of animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bridget Randall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24158506"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T17:37:31Z","content":"Why isThe Bible actually has much to say in regard to animal abuse. In the beginning, God created the earth and all the creatures on it to be under the authority of humanity. He entrusted these beautiful elements of His creation to our care (Genesis 1:26). Our sinful nature causes us to abuse these things, sometimes without even realizing it. Yet, God expects the Christian, above all others, to be sensitive to all of His creation, knowing that exploiting or abusing it shows a disrespect for God Himself. Abuse of anything that God made is not the character of God, but rather of the Evil One. this important to you? (Optional)","like_count":0,"author_name":"Irene Coleman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1443291"},{"created_at":"2013-02-22T13:00:03Z","content":"Food animals give their lives for us.  Lets give them a reasonably happy life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ken Clarke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41990524"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T12:42:31Z","content":"No animal should have to live this way for a human.  Will no longer eat pork.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tom Hammond","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3110792"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:13:30Z","content":"Why are we still treating animals this way? Whether for food, security, or as companions, cruelty has no place if we consider ourselves \"superior\", \"advanced\", \"intelligent\". ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stella Powelczyk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7351058"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:54:38Z","content":"This is sad, and inhumane.  No animal deserves to be treated this way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Annette Whillier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19813404"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:48:45Z","content":"This brutality against animals has to stop, the treatment of these poor pigs is outrageous. Punish the responsible companies by not purchasing a single product from their businesses. Thanks for exposing the truth. Bob ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bob Georgiev","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36188034"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T20:55:05Z","content":"This abuse & torture is unnecessary!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hassel Aviles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27716197"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T18:13:47Z","content":"I think we are the real \"animals.\"","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie Galati","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8444684"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T01:45:26Z","content":"I have seen personally how these poor animals are treated and it is definitely a crime against innocent creatures the way they are kept. Please help them right away. Pig farming must change. We have to help them......","like_count":0,"author_name":"linda johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13991314"},{"created_at":"2012-12-31T22:56:44Z","content":"I will be spreading the word to my entire family and friends in Canada to boycott your stores until you stop buying your meat from these torture chambers!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23520467"},{"created_at":"2013-01-21T01:32:43Z","content":"All forms of life deserve to be treated with dignity. This is absolutely disgusting. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kanjana Brodie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22989695"},{"created_at":"2013-01-28T20:49:34Z","content":"reasons like this is why i miss our local farmer. the Government worked so hard to eliminate. Now we have animals raised like this, fed steroids. It is a disgrace to have animals treated like this in this day and age. What is wrong with people that let this even begin to happen. animals should be left to graze and live there life be it for food or not they should be cared and fed properly.They save our lives but we can't take care of there's even for a bit knowing there our food source.\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erin Fenton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36255315"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T23:02:32Z","content":"It is wrong, cruel and we know better and should do the right thing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eddie Davids","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37200951"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T01:24:11Z","content":"This horrific treatment of animals angers me in a way I didn't know was possible. I am outraged that this type of treatment of animals even occurs, and it makes me ashamed to be human. We need to put a stop to this NOW! If we need to raise animals to eat, we must treat these animals with kindness and ensure they are raised in a comfortable environment, and when it's time for them to be killed,  it must be done in the most humane, quick, and painless way possible. After all, their life purpose is providing us with food. The least we could do is ensure they have a good life while they're still alive. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5138489"},{"created_at":"2013-01-04T06:27:56Z","content":"NO ANIMAL SHOULD HAVE TO LIVE LIKE THIS.....AND NO ANIMAL SHOULD HAVE SUCH A CRUEL DEATH.","like_count":0,"author_name":"HEATHER BINGHAM","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28350792"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:24:22Z","content":"I hate animal cruelty ...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marjorie Gevaert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19952357"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:37:10Z","content":"no animal should be tortured in the name of eating.? Vegan is the way. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Irma Romano","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36973187"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:40:48Z","content":"i dont beleive in abuseing animals i had a pet pig growing up and he was awesome he was smarter then some humans we had alot of fun growing together there a very smart animal","like_count":0,"author_name":"suzanne corbett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27806772"},{"created_at":"2012-12-25T00:15:14Z","content":"No living creature should be treated like this