olve as enlightened human beings.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Oksana Mykytczuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31590011"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T03:36:23Z","content":"Respect for life is the most important value we have. Without respect and kindness toward the most defenceless and innocent forms of life, it is a short step to the destruction of the environment, mass shootings, rape, torture, and other brutal atrocities. Every action we take says who we are as people. if we must take other's lives for food, let's at least treat them with respect and kindness while they are alive and be grateful for their sacrifice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"julie iamarino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36305544"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T19:06:34Z","content":"La souffrance des \u00eatre vivants et sensibles est insoutenable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"martinne girard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7172187"},{"created_at":"2013-01-24T20:33:35Z","content":"A simple request: Have a freaking heart!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"gwen woodcock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1254846"},{"created_at":"2012-12-27T00:08:57Z","content":"Stop supporting factory farming, it's cruel and unnecessary! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy Kirkland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32622231"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:43:44Z","content":"Because its appalling and barbaric..This should be stopped!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Adams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36254160"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T14:02:27Z","content":"No animal should be treated like this. It is all about the money. The people who have done this should be treated the same way!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rhonda  Doty","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26442438"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T00:46:19Z","content":"Because I have respect","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cameron Mulder","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27581058"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T0