ood sources are also the SAME company making our food and making MONEY off our food. We are not only poisoning and hurting animals we are allowing OURSELVES to be poisoned. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lily Hall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39523497"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:23:51Z","content":"No animal should be subjected to this kind of abuse. I nearly broke out in tears watching this, and this needs to be stopped.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shannon Amero","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36321056"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T00:05:51Z","content":"Those sick fucking people need to be treated the way they treat those poor babies ! Please help to stop this!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"kimberly colclough","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35757993"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:17:43Z","content":"This needs to stop!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erika Hirsch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/623829"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:55:47Z","content":"We should not stand for any cruelty or abuse towards any sentient being!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Stringer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/51000"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:15:46Z","content":"You eat these animals, what could be crueler.","like_count":0,"author_name":"thomas elwell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28238303"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T04:16:46Z","content":"This cannot go on!  What is wrong with these people!  These are living creatures that should have be treated with humanity and dignity!  Disgraceful!  They should be severely punished for their actions!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lana Crowe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36494506"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T07:49:24Z","content":"It's simple. Stop.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ryan Andrew Murphy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25004836"},{"created_at":"2013-04-14T05:15:40Z","content":"I loved bacon, but I hate seeing animals abused or hurt ","like_count":0,"author_na