n without anaesthesia are needless cruelty.  Please get in line with world opinion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"William Colby","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36324097"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T23:20:57Z","content":"Pigs are intelligent animals, deserving of our love and respect.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Hawes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25096887"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T01:29:45Z","content":"Pigs are smarter than most humans. Watch any sit-com and the type of people who watch if you doubt this. And we call ourselves human. Well this is not humane.","like_count":0,"author_name":"kathleen eckhardt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36488262"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:40:45Z","content":"Shame on Canada for allowing such cruelty! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pamela Graydon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12979193"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T09:59:33Z","content":"This is heart breaking ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tara Yates","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36350659"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:15:55Z","content":"I don't mind paying more for better animal living conditions. Stop doing this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maxime Santerre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29881971"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:07:14Z","content":"The pain suffered by an animal is the same as that suffered by you.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicholas Evans","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30714571"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:24:27Z","content":"Pigs are shown to very intelligent and social creatures, the least we can do is let them live their lives with dignity. I buy only locally raised meat after seeing the barbaric conditions in these factory farms.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jon  Pickle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12463875"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T18:30:26Z","content":"I am ashamed and consider seriously stopping to eat pork","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sylvie Bergeron","author_url":