t by living vegan.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane McNally","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1991709"},{"created_at":"2013-02-27T21:11:02Z","content":"Animals do not deserve to be mistreated! They feel emotions like we do and deserve respect. If you eat pork, think about the disease, antibiotics and infection that end up being transferred to you when you ingest that pork....how healthy is it?!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Samantha Barber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/42358518"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T18:26:57Z","content":"Because pigs are so intelligent and loving.. it is just a horrible life for any animal..","like_count":0,"author_name":"MICHELE TODD","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16778488"},{"created_at":"2013-01-10T16:28:36Z","content":"It is absolutely imperative that these types of mistreatment towards the lives of animals who share hearts and brains just as we have them ourselves. They don't deserve this atrocious behaviour being forced upon them and exploited from them. And no human should have the mental capacity to inflict torture upon animals and then eat them. Humans allowing this to continue, and supporting the industries which sell this flesh to you is not on, it needs to stop. Please stop eating animals and allowing these acts to continue. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Breanne Vea","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28275305"}]}
