k but see no reason for such disgusting treatment when humane methods are possible and used by others.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wendy Maurice","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39648479"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:20:47Z","content":"For obvious reasons","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Roth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36307223"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T18:49:32Z","content":"Cruelty to any lving being is outrageous, how can ones heart feel no emotion. i understand we as a race eat meat but cruelty is absolutely unnecessary.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michele  Cassady","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29947044"},{"created_at":"2013-05-09T21:48:17Z","content":"This is a disgraceful practice. Stop torturing animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shauna McCartney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16517520"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:41:07Z","content":"this degree of suffering is unacceptable ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patti McCormick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36317997"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:08:58Z","content":"How could it not be important....gentle, extremely intelligent pigs are being tortured....It makes my stomach sick","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ruth Fortin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8297248"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T01:15:25Z","content":"Please, please stop using cruel companies.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Szura","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16943608"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T08:12:28Z","content":"I am a farm girl who values life and is a holistic nutritionalist that believes in farm raised quality life for any creature, even ones we eat.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brittany Geschwendt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36346647"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:36:39Z","content":"\u201cYou can easily judge the character of a man by how he treats those who can do nothing for him.\u201d\u2014Malcolm S. Forbes","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isolde Van J