mal is raised that way, it's fear and pain will reverberate throughout the globe.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mark Barnrd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36617257"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:19:14Z","content":"I believe killing animals is not needed to survive. I've been a vegetarian for last 31+years, at age 55, I'm physically and mentally fit. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Harjit Singh Pabla","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/harjit-pabla"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:44:47Z","content":"That pig is looking into my soul, and it feels awful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Derek Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15982972"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:29:43Z","content":"This is sad on so many levels, people eat these poor animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amal zahra","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26908273"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T17:54:25Z","content":"do i really need to explain why treating animals with respect is important to me?","like_count":0,"author_name":"garen jemian","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36655394"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T04:39:49Z","content":"8 months ago I carefully cut meat out of my diet after learning about the horrors that is today's food production system. We will stand and fight against this genocide; we will fight for the rights to food, water, shelter and a safe environment. This has to stop. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"danielle nantais","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37056162"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T05:08:01Z","content":"Because I hate seeing any animal tortured. I don't eat pork but I do feel pain for these pigs & all other animals. This is so uncalled for!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Becky McCrary","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6484062"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T22:15:26Z","content":"My partner working in one of these places  that do this. The stories he would tell me were horrifying. He was taught to kill. He told me of how they would bounce the baby pigs' heads off the cement floor, hit them in the head with a steel bat or if having a bad day or a pig was not cooperating they would just kill a pig for no reason and how no one there cared for the well- being of these animals. It made  my partner feel like he was worthless, he got really depressed and was always upset with his life and the consent daily killing. He would come home and take it out on his family. Finally he had to go on Medical Stress leave and eventually got his doctor to say that he was not allowed to go to work in a place of this manner. I believe that every animal out there be pig, cow or chicken be kept in cages that are big enough for them and be able to have free- roam time. The things that go on in these places are horrifying and cruel and need to be stopped, not just for the animals but for the people that work there as well!","like_count":0,"author_name":"heather cormier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26942016"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T12:34:23Z","content":"Uncivilized and barbaric.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda MacFarlane","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31170748"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T12:49:05Z","content":"I am truly sick of the way that we allow animals to be tortured for our gain.  The only thing that makes me sicker, is the apathy that most people take towards it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dennis Galley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29052846"},{"created_at":"2013-05-02T21:39:03Z","content":"i like pigs","like_count":0,"author_name":"mihir kakkar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47456692"},{"created_at":"2013-05-14T18:49:37Z","content":"This is so wrong\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rocio Gomez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50574013"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T22:52:06Z","content":"\r\npigs are people too!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sylvain Cholette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36537916"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T13:58:38Z","content":"Abusing a living being is wrong","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jamie Wilson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36447416"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:07:22Z","content":"No living creature deserves to be tortured and abused. I will not shop at a place that supports such inhumanity. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna Wangler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36289126"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:48:18Z","content":"they are giving their lives up, and should NEVER be treated badly.... NEVER!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Chong-Kwan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2558235"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T20:21:41Z","content":"Obvious","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Roth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36312071"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:30:36Z","content":"To end animal cruelty..!!!\r\nStop it Now!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marisol Dom\u00ednguez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36327800"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T02:04:38Z","content":"animal cruelty","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maxime Laferriere","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36332507"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T08:12:29Z","content":"Because all life is beautiful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"savvy angeles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37122409"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:58:04Z","content":"It breaks mu heart to see this cruelty!! I am proud vegetarian !!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"ulker nur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33937318"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:24:38Z","content":"How can anyone not see that these beautiful animals are every bit as sacred as we \"humans\" are.  With love and compassion to each and every one of them !  May we learn in the New Earth that lies just ahead...to trust and love unconditionally as every member of the animal kingdom does...naturally !!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Lee MacKinnon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36119962"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T03:17:52Z","content":"I have just watched W5, Dec. 08/12 and I am so appauled at what I saw.  I am so saddened at this practice, so ashamed that this is common practice in Canada. What must we do to change all of this quickly and forever?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janice MacInnis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24678952"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T23:06:47Z","content":"I love meat, but I love animals too - and I want my meat to have had a dignified, clean life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Marsano","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33611308"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T00:08:59Z","content":"animals should live a human life and be slaughtered in a humane manor ","like_count":0,"author_name":"SAM AABEDI","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35472215"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:12:53Z","content":"I saw the show on this. I'm disgusted that this can happen in Canada!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Sevigny","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20831247"},{"created_at":"2012-12-26T15:26:36Z","content":"I believe it is our responsibility as people of conscience  to protect and care for those who cannot do so for themselves. I am not a vegetarian...I feel we are intended to be omnivorous. But there is no excuse to not treat these animals as humanely as possible while they are alive. Our household has stopped buying pork until we are satisfied that profound changes are made in the industry.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Penticton's Flashback","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12066057"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:38:14Z","content":"Animals deserve to be treated with respect. Just because we are raising them for food does not give us the right to treat them as an inanimate object. Animals deserve our respect too.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica McLeod","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33288270"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T23:27:00Z","content":"All living creatures have the right to live and be treated humanely...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen Liba","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37159303"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T19:31:02Z","content":"Pigs are loving smart animals, and people take advantage of the wall of communication between animals and humans","like_count":0,"author_name":"ginger broatch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36659502"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T03:20:39Z","content":"I don't buy pork from pigs raised in cruel confinement. I raised pigs on a small farm. Pigs need freedom to move around! Animals deserve humane living conditions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paula Johanson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20946344"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T07:29:07Z","content":"I work for Sobey's. I've always been proud of the fact that they took the time to put monuey back into the community by buying locally as much as possible. But please, Sobey's don't let someone like Safeway trump you in the ethical business practices. You're doing pretty good so far, but don't support the piggy concentration camps. In the long run. it's just bad business. Bad conditions. Bad product. Mad customer. Refund. Sick piggy, sick customer. Lawsuit.  \r\nIt might save money in the short term, but you always get what you pay for.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ben McFee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29432099"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T01:19:53Z","content":"How someone can do this is completely sick. I hope you rot.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laurel Woodward","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32173490"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T01:27:27Z","content":"Because torture on any species human or animal is wrong...and I will never be a soul eater.","like_count":0,"author_name":"michelle freer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1515177"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T21:33:15Z","content":"Cruelty to animals has no place in this world. Our Native Indians from long ago respected the hunt and the animal. We will continue to farm and need to sustain ourselves but we do not need to be inhumane when we do so. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mandy Conlon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31696017"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:37:27Z","content":"one day we will all stand before God and account for our deeds here on earth - to all of His creation","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Hurlington","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1497353"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:06:25Z","content":"This archaic and embarrassingly cruel practice has to end.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Arielle McKeown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22734898"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:10:44Z","content":"Je suis contre la souffrance animale .","like_count":0,"author_name":"J\u00e9rome Fonteneau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21834860"},{"created_at":"2013-01-09T04:56:43Z","content":"I do not believe in Animal cruelty and i find it disappointing that I work for one of these grocery giants that are doing this. Action must be taken. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leandro D","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14702478"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:58:04Z","content":"You are what you eat...it is said.... For us to condone how these animals are forced to live and die is unbelievably inhumane.  The places they are contained are run by people is this not true, and these people hae to become either hardened to this experience as well or they would quit... we are raising people that have this inhumane hearts and minds and that's not good either.  they people that own these places also have to condone this , The fact they can is also a very bad sign for society and then the people that  manage these places, buy these products.. they are removed somewhat but if they know.. they are also hardening their hearts turning their heads away from the truth........so it comes to the consumer who then buys these products..trusting in the good name of these companies?  Or just wanting to save money?  Well if it was a bit more expensive everywhere, it wouldn't be thought twice about.  Why is it that even Europe has the sense to do things differently when they have less land and more people?  I for one will never buy   products from animals in these places ever again until this stops.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daphne Mennell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9200421"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:48:57Z","content":"I think that it is illegal and unethical to treat all animals with violence.  After reading this article and after having seen the video on CBC, I can't imagine myself eating meat again.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cristina Pineda","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35856400"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T06:37:14Z","content":"Not something I want to have happening to the food I eat, regardless of intelligence. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"mikael raheem","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7370269"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:39:34Z","content":"All animals, whether they're destined for our food supply or are being invited into our homes for companionship, deserve to be raised humanely and shown the utmost of respect. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Darcy Munson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27952308"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:33:03Z","content":"Pigs are creatures just like us - they love, they like to enjoy nice weather, they even like to swim for fun! If we must use animals for food, they deserve to be well-treated for their short life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Winchester","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1984785"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:54:53Z","content":"N'encouragez plus cette pratique cruelle!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ariane Parayre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36038766"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T22:16:09Z","content":"When I saw on television how crual farmers could be, I wish the same would be done to them as it is done to little pigs and pigs.  I prefer not to eat meat so that they won't raise any animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie-Claude Robineau Marie-Claude Robineau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37040253"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T19:33:00Z","content":"VERY DISTURBING & DEPLORABLE CONTENT in the videos that accompany this petition.  STOP ABUSE  ie. the \u201cStandard Canadian Practice\u201d, against these intelligent & sensitive animals! Tortured\u2026 not to mention .. hormone infested animals, are hard to \u201cdigest\u201d .. & there are repercussions for such things.   Seems there are little psychopathic, Jeffrey Dahmer\u2019s in the making on the farm, & the good ol\u2019 Farmer in the Dell has died. This makes me suspicious of the whole Canadian Farming & Agriculture industry!!!  I don\u2019t trust it anymore.  Europe has more humane laws; this is sooooo WRONG.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura MacDougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36387789"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T19:06:18Z","content":"I don't eat meat and am against animals being mistreated.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane Barber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36613230"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T17:26:13Z","content":"Pigs are sentient creatures. Yes, they may be 'tasty' but they deserve a humane life and death, even if they ultimately end up on our table.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tracey Coveart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36528417"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T02:47:02Z","content":"Assholes these days....","like_count":0,"author_name":"william mcleod","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26128039"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T03:10:00Z","content":"Those who want to eat meat, should be informed... this cruelty must stop!  Free range, family farmed meat is the way to go.  These animals already die for our pleasure... must the suffer in their short lives as well??!?!?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Coulis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2736539"},{"created_at":"2012-12-29T04:23:53Z","content":"Manitoba, and the other prairie provinces have for years dug in their heels and have refused to catch up with the rest of those countries that use more humane methods and treatment of animals. To Manitoba farmers, and producers,animals are nothing but objects and a commodity.   No respect for life .Only respect and greed for the dollar, thus supporting an arrogant, primative, and ignorant way of life. Time to evolve and initiate empathy developement. There are better and more humane ways to do business.","like_count":0,"author_name":"beverley covert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1794561"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T03:58:31Z","content":"Put an end to this today...how can you go home and look into your children's eyes?  Would you show them this cruelty, bring them to the 'farm' for a visit as a family?  Would you tuck them in and tell them the truth about what is going on?  Please have a heart and stand up for what is right...don't wait another minute. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jennifer Dor\u00e9","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33417461"},{"created_at":"2013-01-17T15:02:52Z","content":"It's time we all take a stand and be the voice for animals that deserve better facilities and to be treated right. Besides, what kind of meat are we putting into our bodies having these animals locked up like this. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"april winter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26818967"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:04:28Z","content":"Animal abuse is wrong","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Dudley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36305905"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T15:08:48Z","content":"Cruelity to any helpless annimal I am against.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bernice Melnyk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26886998"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T01:57:54Z","content":"Can't wait to get a sense of closure on this one. Those who harm -- and \"harm\" is just an understatement here -- must know that what goes around, comes around.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Niranjan Shukla","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36489253"},{"created_at":"