nd needs to be stopped. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Dahl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36358013"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T10:53:14Z","content":"very cruel","like_count":0,"author_name":"Icel Jane Dobell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35859974"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T05:05:01Z","content":"it's time.  Were the pigs now....its not right, and we know it!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Kruper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36424517"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T04:04:12Z","content":"Animals deserve a good life; if we're going to take their lives we need to treat them well while they're alive. Animal cruelty is barbaric.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia Outram","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36564828"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T17:32:35Z","content":"This is Discusting and unacceptable.  I don't eat meat.  I believe that we should not as a civilized society be able to allow this kind of treatment of any living creature.  Factory farming needs to be banned everywhere.  Everything has to stop being about mass production.  Please see the need to ban these gestation crates.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Wright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27164666"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T19:10:34Z","content":"health meat for healthy people. pigs deserve better.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melissa Loucks","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37096756"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T17:15:20Z","content":"I am horrified.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andr\u00e9e Simard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31652323"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T16:03:29Z","content":"I can't stand this, it makes me feel sad... like the look of this pig's eyes.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Claude de Guise","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36455042"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:01:58Z","content":"I will not shop at Walmart for the horrendous treatment of ur pork supplier. It is horrific what these poor animals must endure to bring pleasure to ur mouth.","like_count":0,"author_name":"amalia savelli","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1918540"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T22:14:10Z","content":"It is not only female pigs in gestation cages that live a tortuous life and inhumane slaughter.  The cattle and chickens and turkeys raised on factory farms are also treated badly, like a non-living thing.  It is not surprising that owners of these factory farms view their workers in much the same light and force them to work in unsafe conditions with very little pay.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Villalta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30364748"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T18:46:26Z","content":"Because its simply sick to treat animals this way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"chantal rafaelle lafrance","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36602838"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T05:08:36Z","content":"I use to work on a pig farm and each pig has its own personality and I tried to give them a good environment and life while they were with us. I'd hate to think that after they leave the breeding complex they are tortured, that's not right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ozzy Crooker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24237926"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T01:04:08Z","content":"No living creature deserves to be tortured and subjected to the abuse these animals have suffered.  How can we allow  this?  I will never again shop at Sobeys, Superstore/Loblaws, Metro, or Walmart!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Evans","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10932740"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T01:29:14Z","content":"If we dont stand together and make this change, what is to become of us? Proud Vegetarian!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sharon Williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36330823"},{"created_at":"2013-04-11T13:27:28Z","content":"Because every life has value.","like_count":0,"author_name":"dee campbell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6613975"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T03:06:34Z","content":"\u201c The greatness of a nation and its moral progress can be judged by the way its animals are treated. \u201d.\r\n\r\nGhandi","like_count":0,"author_name":"Corinne Viau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36335553"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:10:48Z","content":"Animals need to live and die with dignity.  I am not a vegetarian, and believe that animals used for human consumption should be raised in open fields and large enclosures (free range chickens and beef) regardless of the extra cost to market.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Murray Byers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13254524"},{"created_at":"2013-01-16T05:33:11Z","content":"\r\nThis is so terrible, it hurts to read about it. let alone watch as this investigator did....Help us stop this hhorrible abuse....Stop. now...for the mercy of the animals...KG","like_count":0,"author_name":"kathrryn gress","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8338979"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T05:01:42Z","content":"Cruelty to these animals should not be tolerated.","like_count":0,"author_name":"IRENE GARZA","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6313083"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:42:29Z","content":"I hate cruelty toward any living thing","like_count":0,"author_name":"eileen azar-connor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34564728"},{"created_at":"2013-03-22T01:53:55Z","content":"It disgusts me and hurts me that animals are being treated with this utter disregard. Anyone who is fortunate enough to have an animal as a member of the family will attest to the fact that animals aren't so different from humans: they're loving, nurturing, and demonstrate very similar emotional behaviours that humans do. Show some compassion for these poor creatures.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Lalonde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44909172"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:19:31Z","content":"I grew up on a farm, but our pigs were well fed and had lots of room to run around.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16254711"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T23:31:03Z","content":"A question that hardly needs answer - living things deserve to be treated humanely, even if (perhaps especially if) we are going to eat them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pete Harned","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29097533"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:03:24Z","content":"If you have to eat meat, at least eat meat that's been procured in a humane way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bryan Mallinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30990860"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T16:49:41Z","content":"Regardless weather or not the animal will die so we can eat, the animal needs to be treated with dignitiy and respect, just as we do. What kind of ppl do that? I hope one day the same treatment is put upon them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"crystal clinton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36652346"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:53:55Z","content":"Because no living thing either human or animal should be allowed to suffer unnecessarily.  I no longer eat veal and will not now eat pork unless its organic or from animals raised humanely.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marge Campion","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17113322"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T14:49:19Z","content":"Pigs are someone, not something.","like_count":0,"author_name":"M. Michelle Nadon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26749442"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:01:15Z","content":"Pigs are smarter than dogs, have emotions, and feel pain. We are moving in the wrong direction by treating these sentient beings as mere commodity.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pamela Kerr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2593054"},{"created_at":"2013-01-03T16:39:30Z","content":"This is unaccetable in any place, time, or in any way. I was was utterly shocked and repulsed at these practices. \r\nIt makes me wnat to throw up.\r\nThese beings have feelings as do we--to think otherwise is medieval. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathryn Barkman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7480672"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T20:29:31Z","content":"This matters because we can make a conscious choice not to cause pain and suffering. It's the right thing to do.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Pinker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36392464"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T01:40:43Z","content":"Animals (other than humans) have the right to exist just as much as humans. This is an utterly despicable way to treat a living being.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nathan Perlstein","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36952926"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T18:05:45Z","content":"totally disgusting! humans  who watch this should be outraged.","like_count":0,"author_name":"JOHNNY FORNAROLO","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36227900"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T06:47:17Z","content":"It horrifies me, the way we treat food animals in Canada.  I went vegan 15 years ago because I could no longer stomach the suffering we inflict on these beings.  Please stop the cruelty.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Richard Selin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23170539"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:51:34Z","content":"Beause it makes me sick to my stomach that animals are treated like this, i have stopped eating meat because of this, i feel very strong about the torturing of any animals !! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Johannsen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16708850"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T21:33:38Z","content":"just because","like_count":0,"author_name":"ronna mcmahon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36548277"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T14:42:11Z","content":"I cannot believe that in 2012 humans can behave in such a barbric manner. IT MUST STOP ! We can do so much better and in so-doing feel and be better.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Micheline Beaulieu","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36449792"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:53:06Z","content":"These animals don't deserve this type of cruelty!!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36292242"},{"created_at":"2013-01-25T16:22:48Z","content":"As a veterinarian I am appalled by the lack of concern for the welfare of pigs housed in intensive farming conditions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Downes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14925628"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T05:37:43Z","content":"This is Terrible, Get rid of the Crates....Canada Against Gestation Crates!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tammy GUY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2234792"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T00:15:18Z","content":"I absolutely detest any form of cruelty towards our animal friends. I wish that farmer could've switched places with that poor, helpless pig. Perhaps he would've changed his barbaric ways.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jasmine Baksh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7553069"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:20:22Z","content":"the torturing of any LIVING creature is a CRIME!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Steven M Giles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26716310"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:51:01Z","content":"Factory farming is not only inhumane and cruel, it also causes significant harm to our environment through greenhouse gas emissions. It also decreases meat prices, which promotes unnecessary overconsumption of animal protein. It doesn't have to be this way - the world can be a better place.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adriana Cimo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27362075"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:24:48Z","content":"I can't believe how cruel these people can be, there has to be something wrong with your head to think doing something like this is okay. \r\nImagine the tables were turned, how would you feel? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brittany Fox","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27429298"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:30:21Z","content":"It's sickening how someone could see this and not want to prevent it. It just shows how removed the people in charge of the decision to raise animals in these conditions. If they saw in person the kind of living conditions the animals go through you'd hope they'd stop it immediately. Unfortunately not everyone feels badly for these living creatures. I hope together we can end inhumane treatment of animals and people. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ellyn McTavish","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27226431"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:49:09Z","content":"Im human and I care","like_count":0,"author_name":"April Gillard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36797504"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T12:26:54Z","content":"this is not how god would want his beautiful creatures to live. We should put the greedy corporate managers in the creates let them see first hand what kind of life this is!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charles cowell III","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36356989"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:33:32Z","content":"Putting any sort of living animal destroys what we call our 'humanity'","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adam Kujawinski","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21387559"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:21:43Z","content":"There got to be a better method and allow more freedom ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Douglas Knutson ","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13041715"},{"created_at":"2012-12-26T16:12:44Z","content":"We are living beings just like pigs. WE CAN CHANGE THIS!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jesse Singer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32653194"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T22:53:32Z","content":"I have always admired pigs","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ted plummer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34582007"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:44:52Z","content":"We just can not stand that torture to speechless animals. This is not a human way to grow animals at the farms.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tatiana Mukhina","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30192865"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T15:54:55Z","content":"Pigs are intelligent beings and have to be treated like that.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marja Kokkonen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1504448"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T16:07:37Z","content":"Disgusting to treat ANY animal this way in this day and age !!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dane  Barringer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26357880"},{"created_at":"2012-12-29T03:27:55Z","content":"Was this animal given feet just to lie on them?  How some people just love to go against the flow.","like_count":0,"author_name":"ilene yawney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20744415"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T18:03:40Z","content":"Cruelty to any living animal needs to stop, we are human are we not?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathy Kauth","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26928816"},{"created_at":"2012-12-31T18:50:07Z","content":"I love animals,and I want to make sure they are treated right.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jasmine Link","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36873162"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T21:58:19Z","content":"it has to stop and is discusting","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debora Gordon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36549823"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T22:55:16Z","content":"Cruelty, abuse and suffering are not \"part of doing business\", no matter what Karl Kynoch says. Please, DON'T DO business with operaters who commit these practices, and show them it not only isn't good business practice, it will put them OUT of business if they don't change.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ann Shanklin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10446265"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T03:29:55Z","content":"That's disgusting.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andrea Bryer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32208454"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:37:54Z","content":"These people deserve to rot!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Liilian Vegan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10002135"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:58:06Z","content":"THIS IS UNACCEPTABLE","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Vigos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23239276"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:44:31Z","content":"I was shocked to see the treatment of pigs at Puratone. I will no longer buy any pork products in Canada","like_count":0,"author_name":"maggie king","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36291615"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:19:20Z","content":"I am absolutely horrified to find that Canada is no better than the United States. More of these exposures must occur. Only then will our collective meat consumption in this country decline and fewer animals will be needed to supply the demand, making for no need to factory farm and less animals being killed overall. I love that I'm a vegan.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Priyanka Sekhar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3248556"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T20:45:19Z","content":"Every animal deserve to have normal life. This cruelty has no excuse. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Theodora Arsic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36473702"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T23:46:46Z","content":"No animal should be treated that way. Those people should be charged!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Lopatriello","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15278508"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:08:28Z","content":"I would like all animals to be treated just like me, with respect","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jacinte Lavoie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17353477"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T06:32:31Z","content":"I don't believe in cruelty to animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Kirkby","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37119736"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T23:32:37Z","content":"This extreme cruelty no matter what way you spin it be it legal or not . An eye for an eye should happen here , and what's wrong with the goverment federal and provincial to allow such heinous acts to go on in any facility . PLEASE BOYCOT THE MARKETS AND BIG BOX STORES THAT ARE BUYING FROM THIS AND ANY OTHER FACILITY LIKE THIS ANYWHERE!!!!!!!!!!To go vegetarian is a bit harsh but if thats what it will take to put these SICK and CALOUSE people out of business then thats what we should do as a whole . Why is the R.C.M.P. not involved in this if we were to do this kind of thing to a pet holy crap they would be all over you but this UNCOMPREHENCEABLE!!!!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"rob green","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36483482"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:51:01Z","content":"This is a living, breathing, caring, feeling animal. All you have to do is look into her eyes. I am shocked that Sobeys contributes to this. The public has been very misinformed.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cathie Winter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1262966"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:11:58Z","content":"Julie Desjardims","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Desjardins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36564425"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:42:32Z","content":"This isn't just important, it's the difference between absolute wrong and absolute right...the right for an animal to live and die with dignity; protected by human beings from those who harm them.  We stopped purchasing all pork products the day I watched this on W5, so thank you W5, thank you Mercy For Animals Canada.  I'm heartbroken once again by how some people act.  This is Canada.  I'm heartbroken to be Canadian during this time.  I will not partake of these acts.  I will not purchase your tortured products.  You've lost a customer and I hope you lose them all until this ends.  And I ask how those people sleep at night or look themselves in the mirror who tortured, needlessly, those who we should be protecting.  So I guess that' some of why this is \"important\" to me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dawn Lashbrook","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12951655"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T02:42:16Z","content":"Greedy money grubbers!!! Stop the abuse.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tina Takach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8794945"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:03:08Z","content":"I totally agree with Darrell. what an inhumane thing to do. I will not shop at any of these places again until they change it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"robert dumeah","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20184852"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:39:41Z","content":"This cruelty must stop, I won't eat pork ever again! Pigs have feelings too. I say give the same treatment to the humans doing this and see how they like it!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leanne Cowles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26735668"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:49:04Z","content":"I can't stand to see anything suffer.  We have become inhumane in our humanity. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bonnie Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21995040"}]}
