ofollow\">http://www.care2.com/causes/is-animal-cruelty-doomed.html#ixzz2EUQyW</a>\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vie Nystrom","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36146217"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T18:31:42Z","content":"These animals deserve better \"humane\" treatment.  \r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maureen McJannet","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37145908"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:43:16Z","content":"I grew up on a pig farm, they are very intelligent animals and need space to roam.  Their nature is to root in the dirt, and they love to run.  Anything less is torture for them.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Esther Davidchuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30197026"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:49:08Z","content":"Animal cruelty is not necessary.  I happily pay a few more pennies for meat bred in humane conditions.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Alexander","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36851070"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:38:29Z","content":"Animals need to be treated ethically, not to mention all the health hazards these type of conditions breed.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Kellogg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34401926"},{"created_at":"2013-04-08T02:21:06Z","content":"The torture of animals must stop!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Niblock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16637862"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T18:12:27Z","content":"This is SO SICK! How can you abuse animals without any remorse, these animals feel pain as much as we do! ANIMAL ABUSE AND  CRUELTY SHOULD BE BANNED TOTALLY and who ever abused them should be punished the same way!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane Duclos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36228364"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T19:43:47Z","content":"Stop animal suffering for the sake of taste buds. Go vegan!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mike Ginn","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36234258"},{"created_at":"2013-03-23T19:47:51Z","content":"My wi