12-22T01:53:43Z","content":"Their lives are sacrificed to feed our species,  they should be honored. Also, healthier animals are better quality food. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"James Fisher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35959657"},{"created_at":"2012-12-25T05:53:12Z","content":"This is very important to me because I am still a human being, and care about other living creatures. The way pigs are treated on factory farms is disgusting, and one of the most shameful atrocities of our time. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jim  Holyoak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/472533"},{"created_at":"2013-04-18T23:58:41Z","content":"I also worked for Puratone about 7 years ago. I asked all the right questions during my interview about the humane treatment of their pigs. I lasted 2 months and witnessed terrible abuse. Punching, kicking, eye gouging to get the sows to turn in tight spots. I made a complaint when I quit but I'm sure it fell of deaf ears.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Bentley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47939927"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T23:21:53Z","content":"I sickens me to see how cruel humans are to their food. It appears that larger companies sell a product that's is not of good quality. If a pig is abused it must be filled with toxins that are produced when animals has infections, and not treated with care.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Koyama","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9214691"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:03:12Z","content":"Pigs are the most intelligent, most sensual, and most affectionate of all domestic animals,and we, who abhor dog or cat meat . are viciously indifferent to their suffering  that we cause because we are greedy for money and their flesh. How can we sleep at night? What kind of people does this make us? I shudder at the casually sadistic cruelty of our corporate and carnivarous culture and fear for where it is leading us.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Peter Holt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3352825"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T04:59:36Z","content":"Any form of cruelty is an abomination. Humans need to learn to respect what has been given to us to live. \"There is no respect in torturing animals . No food chain that supports this type of action gets my support and I feel their names should be published.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheila Robillard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22921513"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:23:01Z","content":"Because it is so inhumane,so very cruel. Fueled by greed.Hope you can stop it somehow!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joan Harrison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36963974"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T21:38:18Z","content":"We have no right to inflict cruelty on other sentient beings.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kathi Morck","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36331553"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T23:49:13Z","content":"It is important to me-because- I abhor the idea of torturing innocent living creatures!...We know better! While , I do still eat 'some' meat- I am careful to be sure that I only select animals who's quality of life is good.... It is unethical,immoral and criminal to treat our fellow creatures in such a devestating manner....all because of greed!   I will happily pay more to eat meat  and fish -that is humanely raised and killed...\r\nPlease...be aware of this- and the changing times...People do not want BMO food or tortured 'meat'...\r\nThank you, for-listening...and putting a stop to this cruelty!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kate Leach","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31897065"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T19:24:04Z","content":"This is important to me because it is immoral to treat helpless animals in such a manner.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda McEwen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36387011"},{"created_at":"2012-12-31T06:11:43Z","content":"I find this heartbreakingly cruel.It must be stopped.This is not acceptable treatment for our pets! It should not be acceptable for any other animal either!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Manders","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37756368"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:50:37Z","content":"Even if those animal are for the food market (which I totally disagree with), they should still be treat as living being.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Steve P.","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26454310"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T06:28:19Z","content":"Animals are living breathing beings, no different than us humans, except they rely on us to care for them.  They need to be treated with a similar respect and caring.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Bennington","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35398762"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:46:15Z","content":"Animals don't need to be machines.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patti Indre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/333298"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T06:17:16Z","content":"It was shocking to see the disrespect for the animals -- I'm taking a break from pork.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tom Grant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1559038"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T13:44:17Z","content":"We can not tolerate cruelty to other living beings. I can not and will not allow my family to consume products from these kinds of operations. All operations need to be run by those who care for the welfare of the animals. In the end they give up their lives for the profit of others.","like_count":0,"author_name":"P. Brennan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32911585"}]}
