:51:37Z","content":"No living creature should have to endure such sufferings. There's no reason for it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alex Campbell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12858129"},{"created_at":"2013-05-12T02:09:38Z","content":"No animal should be treated with any kind of cruelty!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Stover","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/50315939"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T01:42:55Z","content":"No animal should suffer.whether it i a pig or a horse or a cow or anything else.","like_count":0,"author_name":"eileen  griffin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20767026"},{"created_at":"2013-01-04T12:55:32Z","content":"This sickens me","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dennis Galley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37945601"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:02:49Z","content":"It is a crime to treat living beings as if they were only \"material\".","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dietrich Schwaegerl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20595778"},{"created_at":"2013-03-25T17:58:01Z","content":"From now on, I won't buy anything from any category in these stores until the time that a radical change is done.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Isabelle Tremblay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28891463"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:04:48Z","content":"Please stop buying pork from those factory farms that use gestation crates and treat pigs cruelly.  Thank you.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Mainland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31696367"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:13:11Z","content":"I am ok to eat that kind of food, but if I eat that kind of food, they must treated with respect and dignity.","like_count":0,"author_name":"David-Luc M\u00e9thot-B\u00e9langer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36306659"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:05:37Z","content":"because humanity is defined by the way we treat other animals. I know we eat these animals but there is no reason for them to suffer more than they have too. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ralph Ricciardi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36315470"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:33:10Z","content":"All animals should be treated humanly.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debs Camara","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8747876"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T04:17:28Z","content":"Animals deserve to live just like humans. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vaisakh Kannan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37116359"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T02:30:43Z","content":"This treatment of animals is unconscionable.  How did we sink so low?  All this misery and suffering for an unhealthy meal.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melanie Blake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/246465"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T22:30:30Z","content":"This has got to stop. Meat doesn't have to be like this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Timothy Whelan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12835464"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T03:44:01Z","content":"May god forgive you if you do not put a stop to it as the pigs and I certainly won't!  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denise Geary","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24491326"},{"created_at":"2013-05-14T00:40:46Z","content":"inhumane","like_count":0,"author_name":"arvind dharma","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/44255635"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:37:14Z","content":"Any form of cruelty to our pork industry is not accesptable. These animals have to sacrifice their lives for us to consume.Therefore  forcing them to live in small crates so confined they cant move or turn around is extremely cruel. Please fix this problem. Pigs are intelligent beings and do not deserve this horrible treatment.\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Catherine Heather Graham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20137888"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:58:20Z","content":"I love animals","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caroline Godin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26647317"},{"created_at":"2013-01-17T23:50:24Z","content":"It's disgusting and outrageous. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jerry DeNicola","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2961531"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:49:11Z","content":"if they must be slaughter there has to be a less barbaric way.  Out and out animal cruelty!  Should be banned!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Sherred","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31737973"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:57:43Z","content":"Horrifying. I will make sure that no-one I know ever buys Maple Leaf or Freybe brands of pork. This has to stop.","like_count":0,"author_name":"monica jacobs","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20808954"},{"created_at":"2013-03-06T00:12:35Z","content":"This is my first time signing something like this and after seeing the abuse of pigs, i will be more in-tune. I was horrified to see how the pigs are being treated in canada, i thought we had better laws to protect out animals. how can i enjoy my dinner after knowing this?? can't and won't buy or eat pork.. ...barbaric... ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karina Araniva","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43148953"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T14:16:14Z","content":"No life should be treated this way it is against our creators way to consider this life cheap","like_count":0,"author_name":"arle masters","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36363586"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:41:14Z","content":"Animals deserve to be treated humanely at all times","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephanie O'gara","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15077467"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:13:31Z","content":"The safety and welfare of animals is extremely important to me. If you choose to eat meat that is fine, but you should be aware of how horribly mistreated farm animals are, and we should have better standards in place in order to ensure that their suffering is limited. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole Dionne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1330570"},{"created_at":"2013-01-08T00:02:37Z","content":"It absolutely breaks my heart to hear about how these animals are treated. People need to start being more caring to all living things! Animal abuse should NOT be tolerated!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amber Jordan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25878488"},{"created_at":"2013-05-13T03:39:20Z","content":"This is important to me because I love animals. I cannot believe it is legal in Canada and States for animals to be abused that way, even if they are going to be used in the food industry. These countries, money seems to be most important no matter at what cost. And what type of person could work at these places and abuse animals all day? I hope they all burn in hell and I pray for these animals.\r\n'The greatness of a nation and its moral progress can be judged by the ways its animals are treated.\r\n~ Mahatma Gandhi'\r\nAmen to that. Please pray for these animals.\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Correena Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21799009"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T22:58:06Z","content":"There is no reason why animals raised for meat should be treated so horrifically.  We as consumers have the right and ability to let these farmers and retailers know that we won't stand for this kind of cruelty any longer. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Medina Turner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35147216"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:01:26Z","content":"Animals need to enjoy their lives while growing healthy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Shenton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32033570"},{"created_at":"2013-01-16T17:21:57Z","content":"It is cruel and ugly.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Celina Walker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34934642"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T22:43:30Z","content":"I know a friend who works at sobeys & I shop there too!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cookie Inspector","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34192206"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T17:41:46Z","content":"We don't torture murderers or rapist why would we torture animals that give their life for us to eat? It's wrong!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tamie Killeen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5925345"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T12:32:31Z","content":"This was one of the sickest animal cruelty videos I was unable to finish watching.  The shock and disgust was more than I could stomach.  The only other cruelty videos I have ever had the displeasure of watching was the torturous killing of a domestic dog in China; treatment of dogs (legs tied around back) as \"food\" iin Vietnam; and a horse so traumatized at a Mexican rodeo that it uncontrollably urinated while trying to run from a stall out of the hands of a Mexican \"cowboy\".  Really?  Is this what Canada has become?  Animals designated for our food does not mean we have the right to torture and torment but rather they should be treated with respect and dignity and their lives ended in the most humane and caring  way.  If that causes the price of meat to increase so be it.  If we don't do anything about this we have joined the distasteful, disgusting, torturous treatment of animals in countries such as China, Vietnam and other ignorant countries.  I for one won't have any part of it. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Phyllene Michta","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36442804"},{"created_at":"2013-01-08T23:08:18Z","content":"I love animals","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzie Rae","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38211121"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:02:02Z","content":"Such violent cruelty should be abolished from this world! Stop torturing pigs, you cruel people! Have a heart, for god's sake!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexandra  Dodd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/18021312"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T14:06:20Z","content":"How could it not be important? It is torture.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barbara Manning","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36587209"},{"created_at":"2012-12-25T03:57:15Z","content":"seriously? You need a reason. Just Stop.","like_count":0,"author_name":"carla buttery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37311711"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T23:13:00Z","content":"Because abusing animals is sick and cruel","like_count":0,"author_name":"christine chmelnytzki","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36323815"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:23:06Z","content":"Animals should not be tortured. They are sentient beings like the rest of us. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emma Canham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28788537"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:37:17Z","content":"I believe that we do not have to treat any living creature with cruelty.  We have an obligation to stop ALL suffering regardless of their level in the food chain.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lesley Oliver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27506377"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:30:26Z","content":"Although I do eat meat, I am for ethical treatment of animals, profit margins are not reason enough for animal cruelty.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anthony Palagian","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11663032"},{"created_at":"2012-12-30T20:51:14Z","content":"You are what you eat! Eating cruelty and suffering is not a choice I support!","like_count":0,"author_name":"cindy andison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37049861"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:56:47Z","content":"animals are helpless. the common thought is that this world is for us and our pleasure. It is not only for us. Without all of our animals on land and water we would not survive. Once we understand that we all (all species) need to live together and stop destroying our habitat the world will be a better place! Humans are driven by money which inturn usually ends up harming the world in one way or another. Ask youself if this is almost impossible to watch because it upsets you, then just maybe it is completely wrong!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sonja de Haan","author_url":