etely and totally unacceptable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Cote","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38914450"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:17:14Z","content":"This is WRONG","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Turanich","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36253261"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T13:58:18Z","content":"No animal should be mistreated no matter what their purpose!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Polansky","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30121283"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T17:32:47Z","content":"WHY Is this important to you?  We are caring human beings and should treat all creatures with gracious respect. I am begging you as a customer to demand better conditions for these poor creatures. I will not shop at your store until you do, I have closed my Sobey's Mastercard as well. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laurie Arbuthnot","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8054474"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:26:58Z","content":"I am vegan because of the level of cruelty associated with the meat and dairy industry. It needs to stop.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Devon Hayes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36286595"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:38:01Z","content":"I am vegan, please stop this madness!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deborah Lane","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/649926"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:49:25Z","content":"and Jesus wept ...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alisa Christopher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5168995"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T22:26:04Z","content":"no animal should be kept in a small cage .\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mary Griffiths","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34305067"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T00:03:27Z","content":"I am a animal lover and hate to see any animal tortured not even for food i'd rather be a vegetarian then watch this happen to any animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Dorey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37109557"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:41:40Z","content":"Stop  Barbarian","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie Charlier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14787354"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:50:28Z","content":"There can be no humanity if we can't be humane to other species.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carrie Cook","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25360043"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:08:48Z","content":"I have no plans to stop eating meat. That said, there is no reason for animals to suffer, other than the company's bottom line. I would pay more if that would help. For now, I will boycott pork until Canadian standards change and I will not shop at Sobey's, Walmart or any other store connected to this farm until they use their own buying power to force the needed changes. All life should be respected. Thank you to Mercy for Animals and W5 for bringing this information forward. My family raised chickens for sale as food and our two pigs were beloved pets. All of our animals were well cared for and we still managed to make a profit. There is simply no excuse. I'm deeply saddened and ashamed. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Williamson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36326625"},{"created_at":"2013-04-05T19:44:18Z","content":"I am ashamed to be human. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carolyn Bartz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37477369"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:19:45Z","content":"It's bad enough, through life, to see cruelty to human beings be allowed from day to day. But to be cruel to innocent animals, just because they are weaker than you are, is barbaric and inhuman. We may eat animals in our diets but we don't have to torture them before hand. Where's the compassion?","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Riehl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36026385"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:37:12Z","content":"Animal cruelty is wrong.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rylen Koosees","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29025594"},{"created_at":"2012-12-