ng your company and its products.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Whitney Exton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1905016"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T21:21:12Z","content":"i will never buying your products maple leaf","like_count":0,"author_name":"sylvain lemire","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36316609"},{"created_at":"2013-02-27T01:11:28Z","content":"I am a Cattle decapitation fan.\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aron Kamvik","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16614340"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:28:17Z","content":"I am a Vegan for 12 years now however, I understand that the majority of individuals do not follow a Vegan diet. As long as men will continue to eat meat and meat products, animal under human care shall be provided with the following basic rights, at all time (at birth, while being raised on the farm, while being spayed or neutered, while pregnant, while loaded for transport, while being transported, while waiting before being killed and while being killed) that should be enshrined in Canadian law:\r\n\r\n\u2022Freedom from Hunger and Thirst - by ready access to fresh water and a diet to maintain full health and vigour.\r\n\r\n\u2022Freedom from Discomfort - by providing an appropriate environment including shelter and a comfortable resting area.\r\n\r\n\u2022Freedom from Pain, Injury or Disease - by prevention or rapid diagnosis and treatment.\r\n\r\n\u2022Freedom to Express Normal Behaviour - by providing sufficient space, proper facilities and company of the animal's own kind.\r\n\r\n\u2022Freedom from Fear and Distress - by ensuring conditions and treatment which avoid mental suffering.\r\n\r\nPlease stop the suffering of these innocent animals, change the laws, have Mercy!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Gascon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36327643"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T07:47:01Z","content":"Animal cruelty happens far too often. Let's stop any we can, however we can.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce Megil