{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/911156/reasons?page=2&page_size=500","total_pages":14,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2012-12-09T21:14:39Z","content":"Treating animals humanely for the the life that the animal lives when ultimately it pays the price with its life when we slaughter them to eat is the very least we can do. It should be our moral obligation ","like_count":45,"author_name":"Sherri Delaney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26932307"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T20:42:07Z","content":"I want to live in a country where I do not need to fear that there is an arbitrary line drawn between those who have rights and those who do not. ","like_count":44,"author_name":"Courtney Gottlieb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36237970"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:31:37Z","content":"We are the voice for these poor creatures born in this \"Hell On Earth\"  ","like_count":36,"author_name":"Angela Emery","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36186937"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:54:07Z","content":"This is so cruel and barbaric. It's unethical to do this to an animal.","like_count":26,"author_name":"Mary Baxter","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8011862"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:59:21Z","content":"inhumane physical torture of pigs should be illegal. even worst than how seals are killed. boycott canadian meat indistries folks!","like_count":25,"author_name":"Jennifer McCreath","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/4987966"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T20:33:08Z","content":"This is such a disturbing video and until pork producers, farmers and grocery stores improve the living conditions of these intelligent animals I won't be buying pork.  This is a disgrace to the way Canada treats its animals.","like_count":10,"author_name":"Patricia Smith","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36237398"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:13:54Z","content":"Because no living creature should be treated like this.","like_count":8,"author_name":"Chris Nguyen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36302258"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T20:03:38Z","content":"No animals should endure this torture.","like_count":8,"author_name":"Barbara Curtis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36235590"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:43:15Z","content":"Gestation crates inflict immense suffering on pigs.  There is absolutely no justification for imposing such suffering.","like_count":8,"author_name":"Anjali Choksi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1351188"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T20:46:49Z","content":"There is absolutely NO need to be cruel to the animals we eat....they give their lives so you can eat bacon; is it too much to ask to treat them humanely in life and death?","like_count":7,"author_name":"Sue Maize","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27163322"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:57:24Z","content":"I think we need to treat animals as the beautiful creations they are. People are soo concerned about making money that there morals and values have clearly been thrown in the gutter.It makes me sick","like_count":5,"author_name":"alexandra gorka","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28229174"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T22:22:22Z","content":"These are living sentient beings, not a manufacturers production line and should be treated humanely and have protection from abuse. Farm animals need regulations to abolish this cruelty like cats and dogs, livestock industry has low levels of regulation and oversight, this needs to change.","like_count":5,"author_name":"andrea magee","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1279498"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T00:39:38Z","content":"This information is the most dispicable aspect of human nature born out of Greed. Law's should change we are no longer ignorant to animal intelligence nor should should anyone pretend to be for self serving purposes. Absolutely revolting. They are a disgrace to the farming industry and canadian agriculture as a whole!!! ","like_count":4,"author_name":"Tracy Taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36184072"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:04:44Z","content":"How we treat our animals is a reflection on our society...","like_count":4,"author_name":"Francine Brassard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7598271"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:17:18Z","content":"pigs are intelligent animals who should not have to suffer such atrocities.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Cindy Cardy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7013000"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T01:07:53Z","content":"This is absolutely sickening! I'm ashamed that this is allowed here in Canada!","like_count":3,"author_name":"STEVE ELDER","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36185682"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T21:06:05Z","content":"YES IT IS REALLY IMPORTANT! PLEASE, STOP TORTURING PIGS. THEY HAVE FEELINGS. THEY FEEL IT WHEN IT HURTS... WHY IS IT UNACCEPTABLE TO DO THIS ON HUMAN BUT DOING THIS ON ANIMALS..??? THERE IS NO DIFFERENCE. PLEASE, STOP IT. ","like_count":3,"author_name":"Charlotte Magnan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36240914"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T20:48:38Z","content":"The mere fact that one single animal in the planet is being mistreated makes me sick and breaks my heart...it is one too much. I'm a big animal lover and seeing people torture them and mistreat them made me lose faith in humanity...I will sign as many petitions as i can to help protect thos beautiful creatures from God. Please, let's get together and help those who cannot speak for themselves....","like_count":3,"author_name":"Marta Sznajder","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5219125"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T20:08:27Z","content":"Because regardless of whether or not we close to eat meat we must treat all living creatures with honour and respect. ","like_count":3,"author_name":"Bart Vanstaalduinen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36235908"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T00:42:02Z","content":"This is just not ethical.  We have come so far in the world but this is so backwards.  So wrong.  ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Anika Conrad","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17140248"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:58:19Z","content":"I raised brood sows without gestation crates and I never lost ONE piglet.  My sows lived long and happy lives with pasture, treats and a mud spa.  Their offspring produced lean pork and all of our animals were treated with respect and dignity right up to the time of slaughter.  Factory farming is stressful for both animals and people working in such inhumane conditions.  ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Paula Fougere","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35470881"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:18:21Z","content":"This is pure evil and must be stopped!","like_count":2,"author_name":"Mary Sette","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13130220"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T07:37:37Z","content":"Pigs are such intelligent and sensitive animals, that they are perfectly aware of every bad people do to them.  It\u00b4s simply barbaric the way they treat them. Please have mercy and give them better life conditions.  Go vegan!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Vanessa Leon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33578459"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T20:57:51Z","content":"You need to make a change, no living creature deserve this kind of treatment. I believe that in 2012, huge companies like yours, have to show their customers that they are ready to take a step toward  ethical policies. I also take this change to point out that raising pigs in those conditions is not only extremely cruel but also damaging for the earth. I would like to remind you that factory farming is the main source of pollution on the earth. Thanks for showing a little respect.","like_count":1,"author_name":"C\u00e9cile Le Bourzec","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31266945"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T02:25:03Z","content":"Hey gents and ladies, this is not that complicated. Lets do the right thing","like_count":1,"author_name":"Doug Paterson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21004092"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:41:13Z","content":"We should not be supporting markets that treat animals in such a inhumane way. It doesn't have to be like this. It's disgusting!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Leala Selina","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28660095"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T20:05:27Z","content":"This is important to me because any inhumane treatment of any animals should not be tolerated. Maybe somebody should gather all the wives of the presidents or ceo's of all these companys and stuff them in a crate and breed them like they do the helpless animals. Bad things happen to bad people!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Wayne Rampton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1847233"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:31:43Z","content":"I will stop buying anything from these stores until they human-up!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Susan Meulemeester","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27487512"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:32:16Z","content":"The inhumanity leaves me speechless. I will never again eat ham.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Linda Dettmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11489909"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T12:33:06Z","content":"This is NOT ok! Something HAS to change!  ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lauren Woroniak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36442837"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:14:11Z","content":"This is not right. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Abdullah Tabassum","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25673014"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:30:34Z","content":"There is no room in my heart for cruelty to animals, big or small.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Marie-Agnes Harris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30871615"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:18:04Z","content":"If it can be done humanely, why isn't it being done? We can learn a lot from animals. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jennifer Dickman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25993934"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T06:48:44Z","content":"Pain and suffering inflicted on a three year old child would be hardly less offensive to my personal Consciousness!  Pigs are as intilligent as Dogs and are wondering why these animals...US, are inflicting pain on them while they are Helpless to speak for themselves!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brian McPhillips","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20985342"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:54:56Z","content":"Nobody or nothing, man or animal, should be treated like this.  Totally horrific","like_count":1,"author_name":"Beverley Lotocki","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36968986"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T04:15:42Z","content":"It's FRIG\"N CRUEL !","like_count":1,"author_name":"Marty Valleau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35731099"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T22:16:00Z","content":"I won't eat pork any more unless this changes","like_count":1,"author_name":"Janice Ireland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/20120988"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:22:40Z","content":"Because it's inhumane!!!!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Shawna Baptiste","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36087179"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T04:06:49Z","content":"THERE HAS TO BE A MORE HUMANE WAY THAN THIS TORTURE....ENOUGH IS ENOUGH...IT HAS TO STOP ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Phyllis Michailidis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23124504"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:11:36Z","content":"This makes me cry and hate people.  They've got it mixed up - the humans responsible for treating animals like this are the REAL animals!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stacy Pecorino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35219420"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:31:07Z","content":"No animal, whether a food source or not should suffer in any way. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Leanne Kiernan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27762802"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T14:17:39Z","content":"Animal abuse in any form is totally unacceptable.  Animals feel pain just as humans do.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Verna Dentrey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1839301"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:22:50Z","content":"I cannot support cruelty by buying anything produced by this cruelty.  It's important to me to inform my friends also","like_count":1,"author_name":"JOHANNA HOWARTH","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30120709"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:32:16Z","content":"I cannot continue to support animal torture through my consumer practices. I will have to seek out those ethical sources of meat production. Please become better corporate citizens- stop your support of animal torture !\r\nJulie Dwyer-Young","like_count":1,"author_name":"julie dwyer-young","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27359836"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T21:09:16Z","content":"It is sick and I will never eat pork again until we change the laws and conditions!","like_count":1,"author_name":"jodie morrison","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36596261"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T20:51:38Z","content":"All animals are no less sacred or 'special' than ANY other being. A fact you will learn in the near future","like_count":1,"author_name":"Byron Barwick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21236245"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T23:01:56Z","content":"Those that allow this procedure should be charged under the cruelty act against farm animals. It is within reason in our society we enjoy meat, (ham, beef, etc...)  However, we should respect those animals and give them a proper dwelling to at least live until they are slaughtered for consumption in a humane way\u2026..Period. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Gord McLeish","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36865211"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T17:10:29Z","content":"If you cannot respect a living thing that id (unwillingly) giving it's life for you, whether for food or medical testing, then in my opinion you do NOT deserve it. There is NO reason why an animal has to suffer like this. It's inexcusable. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Amy Thomas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15812960"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:18:55Z","content":"It  makes very little sense to keep sow pigs in gestation crate production. The abuse over long term without doubt causes undo stress and illness which in turn causes the grower valuable income. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Suzann Ritchie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31779832"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T02:08:19Z","content":"We have enough land in Canada we do not have to stoop to this type of torture.Greed is the only reason for this.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Larry Nelson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34439349"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:31:13Z","content":"Treating animals this way reflects on humanity as a whole. I am disgusted by this and if I will stop shopping at these stores entirely if they continue to source pork from these farms (not that I would ever shop at Walmart anyways). I will be monitoring this situation very closely.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mike McLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5074290"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:06:35Z","content":"There is no need for this treatment.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Stephanie Thorson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21022583"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T00:14:21Z","content":"Basic respect for another living being should come before the all mighty profit margin. I am always willing to pay a bit more for my food if I know that my choice has contributed towards a decent quality of life for the animal.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nicole Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36867611"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T04:07:57Z","content":"Because I will pay more for better meat.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Anton Kryachok","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11520763"},{"created_at":"2013-02-10T00:56:52Z","content":"What is my voice for, if it is not to speak for those who have none?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kelly Moncrieff","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41088369"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T23:02:14Z","content":"Gestation crates were developed to take better care of the sows during their pregnancy. However, the designers looked at the pigs as a machine for making baby pigs, not as a place where sensitive animals like pigs would spend most of their lives. What was thought to be better for the pigs has turned out to be cruel.\r\nIt is time sows were treated better and kept in a manner that they can walk around instead of being confined to a small crate for most of their lives.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brian Palmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24280523"},{"created_at":"2013-02-16T04:14:49Z","content":"Animals have feelings too. It breaks my heart to read such a horrific event that occurred. I have decided not to buy pork from the locations mentioned until they take a stand against these pork suppliers.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lara Todero","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31203471"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T02:58:37Z","content":"Greed, apathy and love of the almighty dollar blinds us to every form of cruelty","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dave Mason","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36869984"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:31:21Z","content":"Makes me sick to see what we do to these wonderful animals. Keep the pressure on these stores. I for one will no longer be buying from these stores","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mark Wheeler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29987605"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T22:03:32Z","content":"Cruel beyond all belief. These people should be fired and charged with animal cruelty for how they treat the pigs. This has made me so upset, but I am thankful that people are becoming aware of this now, and hopefully there will be some MAJOR changes. I already do not eat pork or beef,  and I would like to see others change their mind about it.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Christina Bent","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36399677"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T04:55:04Z","content":"We can do more to ensure that our food is produced locally and sustainably.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Darcy George","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16959649"},{"created_at":"2013-02-01T22:47:09Z","content":"Time to find farms with ethics or stop eating meat altogether\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Catherine Tapner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15913921"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T00:32:10Z","content":"Absolutely inhuman and unnaceptable to treat any animal this way, i am an animal lover and the thought of this happening accross Canada in our farm is just shocking and should not be legal or accepted by anyone,","like_count":1,"author_name":"Nathalie Caya","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36183610"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:44:27Z","content":"I'm signing because this is abusive, unnaturally cruel and needs to stop.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kelsey Lagus","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31762187"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:15:11Z","content":"You are on the wrong side of history if you think supporting these death camps for money will bring you long term wealth. People are fed up. I will boycott","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sarena miller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12595165"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:43:45Z","content":"No words to describe the rage I feel at these horrible animal abusers.","like_count":1,"author_name":"janis reed","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36966122"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T20:59:12Z","content":"It's important to know where our food source comes from.  I was so sad when I saw this coverage on CTV.  People never question where we get our meat from.  This is too cruel and makes me want to resort to vegetaranism.  ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Susan  Lock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26481889"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T19:08:34Z","content":"This horror of torture, fear,