,"author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9448415"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T21:21:48Z","content":"This is horrific how can we treat other beings with such disrespect .  I have not eaten pork 15 years because of the obscene treatment of these animals.  Please become leaders and change on what you allow to be respectable behavior from your suppliers.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lori Lelonde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8902610"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T21:35:40Z","content":"This type of torture is simply so unacceptable. Animals are fellow life forms on this planet and deserve humane treatment and respect...","like_count":1,"author_name":"Thomas Paulauskas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36712785"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:26:25Z","content":"there is no excuse for tortruing animals! this is horrific and should be stopped.","like_count":1,"author_name":"allison farr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1224913"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T22:10:42Z","content":"torture is DISCUSTING.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sarah Rost","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10087946"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T15:01:52Z","content":"Pigs are very intelligent. How would you like to take his place in this picture?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kathy VanDeventer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19730121"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:37:01Z","content":"Cruelty to animals is dehumanizing and demonstrate what kind of country we live in\r\n","like_count":1,"author_name":"Shirley Furgoch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17061416"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T04:58:34Z","content":"I will not support an industry that has no mercy on animals. Boycott and shut it down.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Gino Pezzani","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36977036"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T21:12:56Z","content":"This undercover report shows the true horrific story of these poor animals being subjected to very inhumane practices. This is \"Hell on Earth\" with 