manely.  It will hurt us as well in the long run if we choose to ignore the health of our food supply.  Thank you!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Amy Pollitt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16615132"},{"created_at":"2013-01-16T03:41:03Z","content":"There is NO NEED to torture our farm animals, I will not buy any meet unless I can be assured that they are drug, and torture free and free range","like_count":1,"author_name":"Marie Bell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38711336"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:16:09Z","content":"because i would like to be part of saving creatures from abuse and helping other humans to wake up to the atrocities that our specie commits against vulnerable animals who cannot speak for themselves","like_count":1,"author_name":"caroline jobe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7137090"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:59:44Z","content":"These are living creatures and deserve respect and better living conditions, it's bad enough they are living to dye, they sure as hell don't need to suffer the way they are, it makes me sick and the people doing this make me sick  ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Maggie Leclair","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13221747"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T08:42:25Z","content":"All animals deserve dignity","like_count":1,"author_name":"N Phillips","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36734605"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T16:05:59Z","content":"Pigs are very intelligent animals, even more than dogs. We are responsable for our act and consuming habbits","like_count":1,"author_name":"Cyndi Ladouceur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36696357"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T23:22:30Z","content":"I think this is terrible, I have not eaten any pork for over 10 years now because of this reason. Something must be done!!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lianne Guimond","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36866215"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T07:31:22Z","content":"I watched the W5 presentation of the undercover investigation at Puratone.  Our family stopped eating pork and all red meats over 40 years ago for humane reasons.  The Puratone situation just re-affirms our decades-long stand against the unconscionable acts perpetrated against defenseless species all in the name of greed but under the guise of human welfare in feeding our population.  The Puratone situation was absolutely reprehensible to me.  How can so-called caring and \"intelligent\" human beings be so cruel?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Susan Young","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32417773"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T05:22:28Z","content":"Measure of a society is like the treat all kind of life and counsciousness. We live on the same planet, each life influence each other, treating animalys badly, have a return impact on us at the same level.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Caroline Theberge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36729798"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:16:40Z","content":"Its cruel","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jennifer Bradley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10800216"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T04:01:34Z","content":"I want to live in a country where I know all animals are treated ethically. We take their lives to feed ourself. The least we can do is provide them proper care, food and slaughter.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Katty Kang","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26855958"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T18:42:31Z","content":"omg thats horrible those poor creatures , nothing should be treated like this , ever!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Adrienne McLellan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25186742"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T20:26:04Z","content":"The abuse to any animal is untolerable in any form.  The animals that give their lives for our consumption should be treated with some kind of respect.","like_count":1,"author_name":"janet raymond","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36392237"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T21:09:57Z","content":"After learning about the way these poor creatures are being mass produced and brutally treated, I am HORRIFIED that this is happening right in our backyards. I will know longer purchase my pork from any of the grocery stores that use these hog houses. This practice is cruel and needs to be stopped immediatly! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Sarah Mckay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36711581"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T01:00:00Z","content":"Pigs are more like us than we like to think. Imagine if these were humans?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brendan Beckett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9897643"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T00:20:12Z","content":"The cruelty to animals for human consumption is not human. The way in which they are kept, castrated and thumped is a disgrace to the rights of animals. I'm was extremely upset by the W5 video footage I saw and I am very disturbed by it. It's time to change the public views.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Deborah Derocher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36182859"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T18:14:22Z","content":"There is no need other than pathetic greed to treat animals this way. It's so inhumane!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Brenda MacDougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2075913"},{"created_at":"2012-12-08T16:56:11Z","content":"Humans do not need to consume animals products. In fact, we're better off not consuming them. Moreover, animal agriculture causes enormous animal suffering, terrible environmental degradation, and exacerbates global hunger. These are incontrovertible facts. Why would we do something that causes so much harm, when we don't even need to for any reason at all?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Arden Beddoes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6446259"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T18:56:23Z","content":"I will not spend money at a company that condones animal cruelty. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Matthew George","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36848542"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T00:48:46Z","content":"This is cruel and inhumane. Think i will shop at the local farmers market instead!","like_count":1,"author_name":"mike mytko","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29814466"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T00:53:17Z","content":"because there is absolutely no need for cruelty","like_count":1,"author_name":"Peter Geburt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36184890"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T01:14:29Z","content":"i have a pet pig and no way i would even let her think i would do something like this ... this is so sad for an animal to be treated like this just to keep the profits running in the stores involved shame on them","like_count":1,"author_name":"david clouthier","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36868390"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T02:02:16Z","content":"Animals deserve a humane life and a humane death.  ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Erin Skillen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16011319"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:03:54Z","content":"The quality of a life worth living for every living being should be a moral prerequisite.  To put intelligent, feeling, sensitive beings through this kind of life is barbaric, cruel and horrifying.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Tina  Volpe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/256290"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T21:15:49Z","content":"I support sustainable ethical farming and a gestation crate is not sustainable and not ethical.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jennifer Ito","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36829599"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T14:24:05Z","content":"I haven't come to terms with where I stand regarding animal slaughter for meat consumption ~ I eat meat, yet I consider myself a friend to animals.  Hmmmm?  But until I have finally decided to abstain completely from eating dead animals, there must still always be a line that you don't cross ~ in all things!  The way these animals are raised and killed crosses that line no matter how far you stretch it.  Please stop this, if for no other reason than for your own natural spirit (remember??).\r\nSincerely. Karen Bruce","like_count":1,"author_name":"Karen Bruce","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36588149"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T18:42:38Z","content":"Would you treat your dog this way? No, well, please consider that these sentient animals are actually more intelligent than your dog! I have seen pigs in gestation crates first-hand and it is even worse than the pictures. Swine farming has become so artificial that these animals have become very sick. From a humane perspective as well as a public health issue, this must stop. As a Canadian, I feel ashamed. We can do better. If you must buy pork please support free-range and not intensive/factory farms. Better for the animals, better for the farmers, better for the environment, and better for the consumer.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jen Bilous","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31125232"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T14:13:38Z","content":"As major retailers it is your responsibility to ensure that what you sell is at a minimum treated humanely and ethically. If you can't enusre such measures are in place then don't sell the product!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Iris  Fleckeisen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13592902"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T21:59:00Z","content":"Pigs have better cognitive and memory abilities than a 3-4 year old human child. Anyone who can inflict this kind of torture on another sentient being is in dire need of mental evaluation. This company and all workers involved should be charged and jailed for ongoing animal cruelty. Every time footage like this is uncovered, the offending corporation always says,\"this is not our standard practice\". If it's not your standard practice, then why do we keep seeing these videos of abuse and neglect?! This is standard practice in ALL \"meat\" industries. Our standards as a society need to change. This is 100% unethical. These people need to pay for their actions and a clear message needs to be put out there that this will not be tolerated.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Karin Thomas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1225023"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:27:29Z","content":"Animals need a voice!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Rose Ogorzaly","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1262813"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T03:17:14Z","content":"Because living animals should not be treated like automotive parts on a production line.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Omar Salaymeh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33276992"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T21:18:58Z","content":"I do not want to eat meat from animals who have not been treated humanely and who have died horrible deaths.  This is totally unacceptable.  How can we say we are better than the animals we torture?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dr. Dorothea Gaither","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12687275"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T06:31:05Z","content":"Respect to all is important but even more so to the animals that give us sustenance and life! ","like_count":1,"author_name":"David Steyr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27743388"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T02:02:47Z","content":"Because no living creature should have to suffer and die. Life is to precious. Look into the eyes and see the pain and confusion. It is sad! My hope is that soon everyone who hurts animals will have to take responsibility for their cruelty! Life is life no matter the species.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Pamela Givens","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36969317"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T00:24:27Z","content":"There is no need to cause physical and mental cruelty to an animal who is sacrificing his life for humans.  Let them live a carefree life until they give theirs up for you.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Monika Rothenanger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36720343"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:05:15Z","content":"STOPP ANIMAL CRUELTY!!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Iris Schmidt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1143754"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T07:01:27Z","content":"I feel strongly about these appalling and inhumane conditions and feel that it is an awful injustice that needs immediate attention and action taken to stop this horrific abuse. This is not a life for these poor helpless creatures and they deserve improved conditions because they are God's loving creatures.\r\nThey are my loving creatures and I am ashamed to think that this has been going on and covered up. Thankfully some caring sensitive people in this world are trying to expose this injustice but unfortunately they will never be able to change the human condition  responsible for this  greed, sadism, narcissism, and disgusting horrific situation, otherwise this most inexcusable situation would never have been allowed to occur.!!!!!!!!!! This is incredibly heartbreaking and we need an immediate end to this and absolute resolution in every respect.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Cheryl Carey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36344305"},{"created_at":"2012-12-27T21:31:52Z","content":"Raise the animals like the old days!!  Humane and safe meat!!  No GMO corn or wheat either!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Lorrie Provencal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19909450"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T02:26:59Z","content":"Animals have rights and we humans need to respect them. They are part of this world.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Elizabeth J. Figueroa","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2339926"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T20:55:34Z","content":"please stop animal abuse and purchase from suppliers who are humane with raising animals for food supplies.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Shelly Stoll","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24787982"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T02:40:09Z","content":"Stop the torture of animals. Animals feel pain and are sentient beings. ","like_count":1,"author_name":"Paul Roppolo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33413381"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T05:47:17Z","content":"I love animals, these pigs are giving us food to eat without a choice, and they are treated like this. It's barbaric, many people probably think \"oh well, pigs are pigs\", they give us food, I don't think that is the way to treat one that is giving us a gift. Let's change it.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Tori Jardine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15195454"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:08:28Z","content":"Serial Killers are not treated like this! Why are these intelligent innocent animals being treated like this? This is horrid and cruel and animal cruelty at its worst! This need to stop now! Any why the slow death? How come animals are treated in the worst way possible when they have commited no crime what so ever? The hatred man inflicts on them is sickening! No human could live under these conditions and then to be kicked and shocked and forced to walk when you have never had the ability to walk before? This needs to be done to humans who commit such atrocities against the human race, not innocent animals!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kari Mueller","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1002733"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T19:31:37Z","content":"The way we treat animals is an indication of our own humanity.\r\n\r\nhy is this important to you? (Optional)","like_count":1,"author_name":"Alan Way","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36772981"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:13:49Z","content":"i cant explain the sickening feeling i felt as i watched in disbelief how people could ever treat an animal that way,and make jokes as its its funny to hut another living thing.its disgraceful.","like_count":1,"author_name":"melissa hughes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36289548"},{"created_at":"2012-12-17T17:23:01Z","content":"Because I care about animal welfare as much as human welfare","like_count":1,"author_name":"Claudine Gratton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36763244"},{"created_at":"2012-12-16T22:43:44Z","content":