venir; nous en avons besoin! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gilles Beauchamp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26039776"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:36:36Z","content":"This food is not healthy to eat, we waste precious lives for no good reason other than continuing piss-poor social norms.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephen Romanczuk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23154216"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:29:09Z","content":"Stop abuse, torture and slaughtering of animals--Speciesism is another crime against our world. These poor creatures that are predestined by merciless humans to be on our plates are not just some other food group like vegetables. We are made ot the same organic fibers and nerves as they are...We are not so different, except the inhumane mistreatment of those that many deem inferior. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tracie Eliuk-Le Clair","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15743382"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:37:26Z","content":"We should treat the animals we kill and eat with dignity and with respect.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Peter Kowalczyk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26304071"},{"created_at":"2013-01-03T03:08:13Z","content":"All life deserves to live with dignity.  We are the stewards of this planet and it is up to us to take of every living, breathing animal, plant, and insect. This is disgraceful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Judy Gerard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12751848"},{"created_at":"2012-12-30T20:51:34Z","content":"Pigs have consciousness and intelligence.  They should not be raised to be eaten.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eric Ste-Marie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37737498"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:49:37Z","content":"How can you treat any living being this way, nevermind a being with the intelligence and capacity for love as pigs have.  Isn't it bad enough that you slaughter them mercilessly, the least they deserve is to be treated humanely in their short time alive before they are murdered and consumed.  For goodness sake, have a heart.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mikal Cramer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32359640"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:57:18Z","content":"Being born not knowing they would be slaughtered just to become a merchandise is already a suffering describable beyond words.  We should, at the very, very least, make sure that they live healthily, happily and freely while they are alive.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paul Ng","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35382716"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:13:57Z","content":"I love pigs. Science has proven them to be more intelligent than dolphins. I do not eat pork; however, I know others do. That gives NO RIGHT, however, to mistreat and abuse these noble animals while they are alive. I believe in humane treatment for ALL animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Johanna Goldenberg","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27796042"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:22:14Z","content":"Because it is not only cruel but unhealthy for animals to be raised in this fashion, there is a lot to be said for we are what we eat.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Greenwood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9993785"},{"created_at":"2013-03-24T23:59:23Z","content":"This is sad and not needed what so ever, this needs to be stopped","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andjela  Eskic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5138858"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T22:17:03Z","content":"cruelty against animals is unacceptable","like_count":0,"author_name":"antoine baudouin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33099014"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T23:09:36Z","content":"This is barbaric & horrific. It must be stopped now.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deanna Miron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29823899"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:37:10Z","content":"because I am solidarity","like_count":0,"author_name":"Fritzer Valeur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32867975"},{"cr