EATMENT ON OUR LIVESTOCK. THERE WILL BE A SPECIAL PLACE IN HELL FOR ALL OF THOSE THAT CONTINUE TO TORTURE, MAME, ABUSE AND ENFLICT HANIS TREATMENT ON THESE ANIMALS! IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME UNTIL WE CLOSE DOWN YOUR OPERATION!","like_count":0,"author_name":"GLORIA MURPHY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36310118"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T23:10:00Z","content":"I worked on a hog farm years ago. The sows had free run between pregnancies, where housed in large pens for birthing and released back to free run when piglets were weaned and went to farrowing barns. Your experience sickens me beyond belief. I support your effors fully and will quit buying meat at Sobeys or Walmart and tell them why.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Norman Ralph","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34567713"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:42:07Z","content":"Pigs feel anxiety and pain like we do.  If we love animals, we just don't eat them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Betsy Graber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2134262"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T23:24:49Z","content":"Doesn't matter that they are being raised for food. Every living creature on the face of this planet, deserves to be treated humanely.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adela Valdez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16349260"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T00:43:49Z","content":"These animals give their lives to feed the masses. Not that I agree with this, but if it must be, then they should be treated with kindness and respect. They do society a great service. They should be treated better than gold. God bless the people who care and want to make a change. God bless the people who have the power to make a change and DO SO.","like_count":0,"author_name":"laurie mckellar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2406435"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:05:42Z","content":"good greif people, we cant treat animals like this.  We must rise above cruelty to each other and the animals that give up their lives for us to live.",