 animal!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anna  Gruppuso","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13908729"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T06:34:01Z","content":"These gestation crates need to be a thing of the past.  Putting animals through this kind of misery is abhorrent and appalling.  Any companies that support this have a black mark against them and should be boycotted.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Christopher Milne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12163705"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T19:47:14Z","content":"Every living being deserves to live a pain free, respectful life. How can anyone treat an animal that way?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Meagan L","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34456949"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T22:32:42Z","content":"When i saw this, i was discasted by what they have done to those pigs. I really felt an obligation to do at least something to change it...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maja Lalic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36551980"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T23:56:16Z","content":"Do I really have to explain why treating animals like that is wrong?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Matthew Gates","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36556119"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T17:53:00Z","content":"this is just pure evil","like_count":0,"author_name":"donna adams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1470954"},{"created_at":"2012-12-30T03:26:04Z","content":"Stop this cruelty and be responsible to the welfare of all involved!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Good Karm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11754067"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:29:17Z","content":"Animals should not be treated the way this video shows. This video sickness me and I can't believe this goes on here in Canada, I thought we were better then that. People that treat animals like this should put them shelves in the poor pigs place and see if they would like to thrown against the cement over and over again and get steal bars put into there head, like come on give your heads a shake!!!! Just sickness me to no tomorrow! Makes me wanna never touch meat again, thanks.","like_count":0,"author_name":"MISTY HAY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36321432"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:39:06Z","content":"I saw W5 when this show aired and was never so discusted with the inhumane treatment of these animals.....I hate the thoughts of eating pork now and cannot understand how people can be so brutal.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Veinot","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36322053"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:21:00Z","content":"We have to make ethical choices when it comes to the food that we eat. There is no justification for this level of cruelty. We don't have the right to treat animals this way. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Caroline Kemp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1543064"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:37:48Z","content":"Its so cruel","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andr\u00e9 Forsgren","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37012440"},{"created_at":"2013-01-17T23:00:02Z","content":"TO END ANIMAL CRUELTY!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Yolanda Castillo","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38857256"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T04:24:06Z","content":"Killing animals in an inhumane way is wrong and disgusting to the soul. Please stop this. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Samuel C.","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36494752"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:56:24Z","content":"Being abusive to animals,isn't the company,l or many people would like to support, lm thankfully glad this is going around for the people to see,analsowhich companies are supporting this abuse for the bottom line to make money,\r\n.may the CEOs of this company know God is which,shame shame on you.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debbie Classen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28352542"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:20:24Z","content":"I will not step foot in another of the stores named until I hear that they are behaving more socially and ecologically just.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barb Wotherspoon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34799538"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:28:39Z","content":"I can't stomach making animals' lives any worse than they must perforce be!  They're God's Beloved Creatures too and merit no less respect and care!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexander Damyanovich","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7826576"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:45:30Z","content":"I love eating meat of every kind, but the distinction between an animal and food begins at death and not before. Living animals should not be treated as commodities before they are slaughtered, and therefore I must vehemently oppose the inhumane use of gestation crates. Pigs may not be able to speak, but I am certain that they are capable of feeling pain and discomfort. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Austin Gallant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33961877"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T17:55:37Z","content":"when peolpe start seeing what's happening, only then will changes be made.","like_count":0,"author_name":"jenn london","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1609761"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T23:43:06Z","content":"Cruelty must stop!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Doug Kranz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/30131523"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:01:44Z","content":"Cruelty of any kind should never be supported.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donald Gillmore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/33164089"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T20:52:17Z","content":"It's important because no animal should suffer this type of cruelty. How can people be so inhumane. My hearts go out to these animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patricia McCall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36545439"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T20:57:52Z","content":"Stop inhumane treatment of animals.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Philip Chang"