al, factory farming operations! Stop buying meat at these major grocery chains and seek out independent butchers and ASK A LOT OF QUESTIONS! You can obtain clean, healthy meat from small, independent farmers who care about animal welfare. On the farm where I source my meat, I've seen the chickens being raised. I know my farmer. I know my food. And we both respect the animals' lives. It can be done, but we as consumers must each take responsibility for what we buy and put on our plates, or nothing will change. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sibernie  James-Bosch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7819929"},{"created_at":"2012-12-30T16:40:15Z","content":"This Is The Food I Eat, And I did not know pigs was treated this way","like_count":0,"author_name":"trent wildcat","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36535469"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:41:00Z","content":"Mike Walker","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sam Walker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16798770"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:35:06Z","content":"I want to eat healthy food and this is not a healthy way for an animal to be raised.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jan Kreut","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34233654"},{"created_at":"2012-12-28T15:17:58Z","content":"It is a shame to see these animal Factorys and the poor animals have no space.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Beat  Gamper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11766391"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T19:00:57Z","content":"Never eating pork again!\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"alyssa t","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27217036"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:49:49Z","content":"I don't believe these crates are required to supply us with pork.  They are inhumane and extremelt cruel.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katherne Stalwick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17118548"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:10:09Z","content":"Pigs are as smart as a human 3 year old. Now whenever you hear stories about cruelties against pigs, imag