eat others the same way you would like to be treated.  God created animals too.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ana Verde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29288830"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:29:23Z","content":"Gestation crates are inhumane and cruel. It absolutely breaks my heart that in a country as \"developed\" and \"first world\"  as Canada animals are still being allowed to be tortured this way. Gestation crates need to be banned, and I promise not to consume from any of the retailers in Canada that subject animals to such cruel and absolutely revolting conditions.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Giuliana Bueno","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26607902"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:48:15Z","content":"I worked in a pig barn owned by Puratone for a few months and I witnessed almost everything your video showed, and it is truly horiffic to see. I wish that the animals didn't get treated that way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Reggie Kraeker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34312163"},{"created_at":"2013-01-24T08:04:14Z","content":"Cruelty is wrong, always.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louis Cornez","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39285162"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:02:10Z","content":"What a terrible terrible life for these animals !! Cruel and disgusting!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandy Churney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14775200"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:03:28Z","content":"This sort of treatment is incredibly horrid. No living thing should be forced to endure such conditions. While some sick individuals seem to find it humane to do so because the victim is not 'human', it still makes the abuse no less of a crime. We are no different than animals; we are also classified under 'Animalia', so treating these poor pigs, or any other living thing, like this, is no different than forcing a fellow human to endure such an atrocity. My feelings go out to these poor animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michaela Grace","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/gutennachtmeineliebe"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:48:08Z","content":"It's torture for one of Gods creatures.  Not meant to be this way.\r\n ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gemma Chater","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15433124"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:20:14Z","content":"Ghislaine gagn\u00e9","like_count":0,"author_name":"ghislaine gagn\u00e9","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24269668"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T02:54:33Z","content":"I feel that the animals need to be treated fairly regardless of what they are raised for","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashlee Hemming","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36798955"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T02:32:15Z","content":"We need to lobby government to abolish the use of gestation crates as well as expressing to those companies mentioned in this petition to refuse to do business with such unethical and cruel farmers.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandy Catala","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34456414"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T22:12:27Z","content":"Compassion is the supreme virtue and this is NOT compassionate behaviour.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alanna Morgan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12712896"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T13:13:37Z","content":"This is unacceptable. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Wagner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36823939"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T16:31:27Z","content":"because we need to treat other animals with respect, not just ourselves","like_count":0,"author_name":"Noah Gillingham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36952301"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T17:57:30Z","content":"factory farming is inhumane. period.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Janet Field","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12707619"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T09:31:51Z","content":"Do the right thing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy  Peckham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2800963"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T13:45:29Z","content":"\"The greatness of a nation and its moral progress can be judged by the way its animals are treated.\"\r\n        --Ghandi\r\n\r\nhy is this important to you? (Optional)","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Webber","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35223840"},{"created_at":"2013-01-06T03:22:32Z","content":"We, as humans, think we are above other animals (even other humans at times) and have become cruelly desensitized to the suffering of other animals. Just because, we raise animals for consumption does not mean they can be tortured.Another reason to either eat organic meat or not eat meat at all.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sylvia Welke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34405648"},{"created_at":"2013-01-29T23:40:44Z","content":"How disgusting is our culture, our society? Hardly can compassion be found. We expect that foreign governments begin treating their people with compassion and respect. We expect that our own show compassion and respect to us. We expect that our children show compassion and respect to their classmates. So why does compassion stop with living creatures that cannot speak or think on the intellectual level we do? Who or what gave the right to abuse any being or thing with anything less than compassion or respect? Live out your values to the very end, in every moment or your breath is nothing more than wasted. The strongest, wisest is the one who can admit to wrongdoing and try do differently. I will be proud to be Canadian when I see my country uphold true purity, respect and compassion.","like_count":0,"author_name":"lauren schmalz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/19981947"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T01:41:16Z","content":"Animal lover, im a vegitarian but dont discourage people from eating meat but if your going to eat meat there is no reason for this! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maddison Vandenheuvel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36560359"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T10:14:24Z","content":"Animal cruelty