fe is no less valuable than any other, so is animal life. They deserve full moral status just like the less fortunate humans. This said does in no way shape or form give any one the right to abuse, destruction, cruelty and any other form mischief. Animals should not be abused or made to suffer pain. Animals should not be made to watch other animals being slaughtered. Any one that doubts that animals feel any pain should watch a wounded animal. important to you? (Optional)","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stana Kuzmanovic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28041532"},{"created_at":"2013-01-01T15:28:26Z","content":"What is next, stalls for employees, chain them to the desks.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gianna Macias","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2089448"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T23:44:16Z","content":"Living beings that feel fear, pain, terror and despair deserve love and respect from humans.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Javier Blake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16879956"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:43:00Z","content":"because i really care about cruelty  against animals","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah L\u00e9gar\u00e9","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3610274"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T20:30:00Z","content":"Animals should be treated with respect and dignity, and this right to decent treatment is not upheld when animals are exploited for selfish human gain","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandy O'Neill","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6713779"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T01:16:01Z","content":"My principle in life is to be friendly and cooperative with all living creatures. We do not own the Earth, it belongs to all living creatures. What right do we have to torture such animals","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mahmud Wasfi","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17198185"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T02:25:13Z","content":"This is cruelty to animals. Just because they are ultimately being killed for food, their life should be a good quality. If a domestic pet were treated this way then the SPCA would step in - why not the same for all animals!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laureen DeMartini","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28701488"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T21:27:20Z","content":"This is easy to see, the pigs are being treated inhumane. We have to make it stop!","like_count":0,"author_name":"cindy rightmyer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36612223"},{"created_at":"2013-05-03T11:51:51Z","content":"It is unacceptable, a disgrace, inhumane... Stop it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Soni Reed","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10536301"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:35:53Z","content":"Pigs are clean creatures by nature and should be treated with care and respect regardless of their final demise. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wenda Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1646906"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:23:50Z","content":"I will not purchase meat from your stores because of the horrific way these animals are treated! They are living, feeling, soulful beings that are being treated as merchandise! It's disgusting and wrong! It's time to stop thinking in terms or greed and start thinking of all beings and organisms on this planet as precious and not expendable. Mother Earth is not a renewable resource. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carolyn Cartwright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24365536"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:41:31Z","content":"every living being deserves proper treatment, and this treatment makes me sick","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dave Labelle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17242747"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:18:16Z","content":"Animals are giving us their lives for food, and I am sickened by the idea that these lives are in such miniscule rooms during their final days.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bryce Gordon","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17169138"},{"created_at":"2013-01-26T03:14:18Z","content":"Animals deserve to be treated with dignity & respect, like all of us expect, as humans. These poor innocent animals were NOT put on this earth as a food source. STOP KILLING & EATING ANIMALS!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Codi Bauer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39431083"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:17:15Z","content":"I'm devastated and heart-broken that this type of cruelty goes on. It is repulsive to know this treatment exists. Poor animals; so helpless. Anything to put an outright stop to this!","like_count":0,"author_name":"TANYA DI PAOLO","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24744975"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:32:22Z","content":"I have always found it difficult to accept the brutality towards animals that is part of what we eat. It's unnecessary. It's only justification is financial. I feel guilty every time I eat meat because of this, and I often don't buy pork because I know that pigs are particularly intelligent animals, and they suffer as much as any dog in a poorly run puppy mill. I just want to know that the animal I am eating was treated with respect while it lived and died without unnecessary suffering. I know it's a radical idea for many people who have become so distanced from nature and compassion that they laugh at this kind of conscientious objection. But we shut down puppy mills for this kind of treatment. Why should the animals we eat be tortured too? I know in my heart it's wrong and it's just part of my stupid white colonial culture to ignore physical and emotional costs when it comes to economics. thanks for listening to this petition and please be the first to take a stand. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cherie Pyne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1852940"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:55:31Z","content":"Because they are wrong and you are right. I support all that I think is right in this troubled world. Thank you for this opportunity to support what is right.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Andria TETLOW","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35000399"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:37:18Z","content":"I understand that some suppliers are now altering their purchasing but in a not very strong or convincing manner and I have to ask 'Why did you feel it was OK before you got caught?'.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Derek Madge","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17047841"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:10:39Z","content":"I am disgusted and horrified at such cruelty.  I plan to not support the purchase of such products, and plan to pass on the information to family, friends, coworkers, and anyone else I can and encourage them to not support the purchase of meats from these places.  The people doing such horrific acts should be treated in the same manner and see how they feel about it then (when no one will answer their begging cries to free them from the inhumane and torturous acts forced upon them).  These poor, innocent animals have no say in their treatment.  They do not deserve to live their final days this way, and do deserve to be treated humanely before and during their last moments.  It's enough to turn people into vegetarians.  These people must have no conscious...the barbarians who are involved.  Greed is worth this?  Truly?  No amount of money would make me ever treat anything or anyone in such a way.  Get a life...do what is right and stop this madness! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Becky Longfellow","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35441227"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T16:17:43Z","content":"I love life. I can't tolerate torture and abuse to any part of life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tammy Kevwitch","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36372126"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T16:25:19Z","content":"As a Manitoban it saddens me to see the treatment of animals like this in our society.  \r\nWe thank and pray for our food, but how can our empathetic hearts not think and pray for these poor creatures.  Stop this madness, stop this abuse.  There are other ways. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vanessa Cayer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36371701"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T06:39:02Z","content":"All animals should be treated humanly & with respect. This is an abomination! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vickie Allard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12293964"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T22:14:41Z","content":"I am a vegan for 16 years and this is the reason. I am hopeful that human kind will do the rest of proud in near future and stop this crimes against inocent animals.\r\nHow can we believe in god, prey to god and be so cruel to gods creatures. How? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joanna Karapetian","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29682433"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T15:12:08Z","content":"needs to stop","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Halliwell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36520158"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T01:49:51Z","content":"This isn't important at all. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joseph Blincoe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29481200"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T21:16:13Z","content":"Animals are living creatures, we share the land with them.  They dont deserve to be held captive and treated the way they are. This is inhumane and can not go on for any longer. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Ference","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36396167"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T18:53:44Z","content":"No living creature should have to undergo unnecessary cruelty :( The people who are doing this should be put in jail","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Duffill","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36231030"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T15:29:00Z","content":"no words are needed ..just stop this now...","like_count":0,"author_name":"joanne taylor","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27497959"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T22:45:22Z","content":"There is no excuse for any form of animal abuse. I gave up eating pork when I saw the factory farms move into Manitoba. Even though there was a sudden drop in the price of pork and I was poor, I felt it disgraceful to treat a living, breathing, feeling animal purely like an exploitable commodity. It went in the wrong direction. It never fails to amaze me how thoughtless and feelingless business people can be. Ditto for the employees who can stomach working in these places. \r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Teresa Carey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36247107"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T11:06:15Z","content":"Pigs way of life","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bill Frankland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37071129"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:10:32Z","content":"I love pigs and I do not eat them. This is appalling.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hope Brown","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36293417"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:43:32Z","content":"This MUST end.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Deb Hollm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/945783"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:27:08Z","content":"animals are treated with barbaric cruelty, it does not have to be this way","like_count":0,"author_name":"ron mcdougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35513504"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:29:48Z","content":"Why do we not see more media reports on this sort of animal abuse? What is wrong with the media?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pat Lukensmeyer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11855093"},{"created_at":"2012-12-25T13:44:54Z","content":"This is just another example of the uncaring attitude the government has towards all living beings like Idle no more!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ida Lumberjack","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36064478"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T01:50:20Z","content":"This is so inhumane and makes me ashamed to be human. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alyssa Hansen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23014872"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:15:50Z","content":"I have been eating less and less meat.  I can understand that animals get killed for food. But at the very least they should have a good quality of life.  Nothing deserves this kind of abuse and suffering.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katelin Dolega","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7915716"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:42:51Z","content":"Cruelty is NEVER the answer, not even to hunger.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca Stickwood","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13728283"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:54:38Z","content":"The cruelty to animals needs to stop now. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Blair Doty","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37018051"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:26:58Z","content":"This is one BIG reason I try not to eat meat. Look at her face and eyes. She a pig but has feelings also","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Oroviceanu","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29819558"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T03:28:04Z","content":"All living creatures should be treated with compassion and respect.  We DO NOT need to consume animals that are mentally and physically tortured.\r\nLegislation and industry needs to be changed, these animals rights are more important than the bottom line!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle Sturino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36192858"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:35:34Z","content":"Do the Right Thing!!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael King","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28637776"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T06:33:50Z","content":"I care a whole lot about animal welfare that\u2019s why I sign this petition and urge others to do the same, if you care about animal\u2019s you will gladly sign. Merci","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mickey Herouin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/mickeyherouin"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:03:40Z","content":"I am a vegetarian","like_count":0,"author_name":"Craig Boomer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36980701"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:10:39Z","content":"Cruetly is not a necessary part of anything.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debra Glass","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35426814"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T14:31:25Z","content":"This speaks more to the kind of people we are, that we can actually inflict this kind of absolute misery on another living thing.  We're the civilized, evolved species? ...apparently not.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alice Flanigan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36215961"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:14:55Z","content":"I am abhorred with the cruelty and lack of dignity shown to weaker animals.  I vow to stop shopping at the stores listed that support such cruel and inhumane treatment for these suffering animals.   ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hope Boehm","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36253184"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T22:05:51Z","content":"Vegan.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Greg Bruce","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16215883"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T04:37:43Z","content":"Our laws in Canada need to be changed so that it would be a criminal offence to treat farming animals inhumanely.  Canadians need to be made aware of the appalling conditions and procedures that these poor animals live in.  This is the first step towards stoping farmers  doing business this way.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joy Percival","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36260020"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T23:04:28Z","content":"If they're going to die for our nourishment, we should at least treat animals with respect before their death.","like_count":0,"author_name":"marcos  ramos","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1347136"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:10:32Z","content":"I am stunned, once again to read of the barbaric, unconscionable, unspeakablly cruel treatment of these sensitive, intelligent animals. These people are less than what we consider human, they are to say the least, emotionally damaged, and should be forced to suffer the same treatment they inflict on these poor defenseless animals.  I cannot describe adequately the shame I feel knowing I am the same species as these cruel monsters., I will never buy at Walmart again.l","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barbara  Weimann","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2121522"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T21:52:51Z","content":"Other countries have proven that pigs and other farm animals can be raised and slaughtered humanely and still yield healthy profits for farmers and retailers.   Why is Canada always a laggard when it comes to animal rights and environmental issues?  It's shameful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Norbert Kremla","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9934192"}]}
