{"page":3,"prev_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/911156/reasons?page=2&page_size=500","next_page_endpoint":"http://api.change.org/v1/petitions/911156/reasons?page=4&page_size=500","total_pages":14,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:40:03Z","content":"because it's unethical for animals to be raised like this","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bradley Geekie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36329339"},{"created_at":"2013-03-25T01:03:34Z","content":"I hate when animals are torchered.  We know they will die eventually so we can eat but do they have to be abused before death?","like_count":0,"author_name":"wendy hinton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45179308"},{"created_at":"2013-02-05T18:13:34Z","content":"This is not humane","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paolo Mussone","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/40697812"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T23:22:38Z","content":"because the animals that supply the meat that we eat should be respected and live with some dignity.","like_count":0,"author_name":"pat farquharson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26760539"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T20:04:58Z","content":"This is disgrace. The Canadian public will not tolerate such practices. I shall be voting with my wallet.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lisa Logan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36390562"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T18:57:18Z","content":"this is unacceptable treatment of animals it is just wrong ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barb  Chrysler","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15810960"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T16:47:05Z","content":"Don't let profit decide how we should act. These are animals that have feelings and should be treated humanely by us. I will not purchase any food from these companies until things have changed and more consideration given to the animals!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandy Champagne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32568841"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T00:04:25Z","content":"Animals have the capacity to feel pain...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Julie Luhowy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36407150"},{"created_at":"2012-12-31T16:30:03Z","content":"Animals, just like us, want to avoid pain and have a desire to live. They should not have to live a horrible life just so that we can satisfy our appetites!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Thais Amaral","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37777541"},{"created_at":"2013-01-10T16:18:45Z","content":"every creature deserves better than this.","like_count":0,"author_name":"patricia morris","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8212460"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T03:32:35Z","content":"Pigs are smart creatures who deserve a better life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"KATHRYN SAGER","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26679766"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:45:59Z","content":"Demand animal abuse be stopped!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laura Schlegel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/187914"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T21:56:44Z","content":"This is ridiculously cruel. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mihaela Sarbu","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7950043"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:31:08Z","content":"I believe the animals that feed us should be taken care of-look into the eyes of an animal, they are OUR eyes and your reflection is there - how dare you take another living thing without realizing they have feelings,emotions - stop this!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mindy Ponivas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36308034"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T20:06:45Z","content":"Because cruelty against animals reflect what we are as human being, and we're better than that, way better.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charles-Louis Thibault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36269687"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T13:46:09Z","content":"I am disgusted by the torture inflicted upon these defenseless creatures.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paul Dugas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37004814"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T04:27:16Z","content":"On ne fait pas aux autres ce qu'on ne voudrait pas se faire faire.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jessica Cyr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36339252"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T05:47:21Z","content":"Cruelty to innocent animals is obsene and cruel","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ellen Bukstel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24736767"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T16:54:35Z","content":"No living being deserves this.\r\nShame.","like_count":0,"author_name":"debbie balog","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/4992760"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T17:32:34Z","content":"Any human being looking into the eyes of this animal amd \"see\" the cry for help.  I wont be able to forget the eyes.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Leanna Wells","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37143314"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:57:59Z","content":"Animal rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"Linda Vu","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37027068"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T21:21:59Z","content":"Both my adult daughter and I refuse to eat pork (and most other meats) because of the way conventional farming is done. Wise up, grocery stores!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sally Stacey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16853789"},{"created_at":"2012-12-30T22:05:54Z","content":"I find it interesting that in this day and age the cruel manner in which pigs are kept remains acceptable.   Pigs are more intelligent than dogs and the general public and the Canadian government would not accept this cruel treatment of dogs.  Pig organs have been implanted, and continue to be researched for human implantation and humans continue to torture them in ways we would never ever treat a human.  A pig may save your life one day!  Pigs have a nervous system akin to ours and therefore they feel physical pain not unlike ourselves, and yet we continue to keep torturing them in inhumane confinements.  I think pigs are  more capable of conscious thought and compassion than the humans who believe they are not torturing pigs.  I think members of the Canadian government who do not think this act is inhumane or just do not think it an important issue, should be penned in the same manner as our pigs for a one month period and write an essay afterward on why they don't want to be treated like a pig and why pigs will no longer be tortured by the manner in which they are kept.\r\nI think the Canadian government has a lot to learn from pigs.  In fact, I think Prime Minister Stephen Harper should be the first  Government official to enjoy the comforts that a pig stall lifestyle has to offer!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Peggy Kasuba","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35726626"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T15:33:31Z","content":"protecting life, taking care of life. Suffering is not an option and sure not an obligation!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nancy Squires","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36368815"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:13:13Z","content":"pigs are cute and I don't eat them.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mari McMillan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26503607"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T14:51:11Z","content":"this is just not right!!! unbelieveable what we are letting happen.","like_count":0,"author_name":"ishmel hosein","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36216825"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T23:53:26Z","content":"Hey, it's one thing to kill an animal for it's meat..it's another to torture it before you kill it. It's inhumane and you MUST take a stand against it! Think about it..if you were going to be killed, would you like to be tortured first? Also think about what the knowledge of this will do for your company. Sure you will keep the customers who don't know and you will keep customers who don't care..but do you care about the loss of customers who DO care? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Donna Tingley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13062236"},{"created_at":"2013-01-18T15:05:08Z