0:35Z","content":"Every living being deserves to be treated with kindness.  No one should have to endure living like this....even pigs!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Diane MacArthur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1844333"},{"created_at":"2013-01-26T16:57:19Z","content":"Cruel!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra O\"Shea","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27047278"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T21:27:22Z","content":"IT IS CRUEL!!!  WOULD THIS PERSON WHO PUT THIS ANIMAL IN THIS CAGE TRY IT OUT???","like_count":0,"author_name":"Edmay Kamp","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31707881"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T13:04:42Z","content":"Stop toturing the pigs! Let them live naturally, more space around them! They feel the pain, too, just like man.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ingrid Gaida","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37076778"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T01:20:56Z","content":"How we treat our ' food' shows our respect or otherwise for life itself.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denise Bruce","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1209954"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T07:14:00Z","content":"While I feel that the overall keeping of animals to murder them for consumption and money is 100% unethical, I feel there are standards in which to follow, or limits to suffering I wish compassion would move one to consider more than financial gain, and go deeper. These living breathing beings are in pain, confined beyond one's worst guess,depressed, abused, alone, and overused with zero rights. Why? because they cannot speak, for if they did they would say \"please let me go. I need to stretch, I am so sad and lonely. Why do you keep me in this cage for all my life? Can i see my young? I am in so much pain all over my body. Can I take a break please?\" and perhaps someone would have mercy, instead of seeing them as dumb pigs who are only on this earth for the man to use. No rights. This has to change. I know supply must meet demand and we are all working on changing the demand but the stores need to make the first step and ban the cruel gestational crates for starters. TAKE the step and consider their torture while you sleep in your warm bed at night. CARE about the companies you buy your meat supplies from. Do your research. It's the bare minimum. How are the animals being treated before they are left to die a slow death, confused laying on the filthy floor of a noisy factory, never knowing what it's like to play or lay in the sun. No one would want this for their family pet, for their own farm animals if they could have any, and especially not for their living breathing children.","like_count":0,"author_name":"briana stevens","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37212392"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T14:17:21Z","content":"We are still far from being\r\n\"humans\".Rather,we appear as devils.I am an old man,yet\r\nI cried for my brothers the animals.Human domination is a disaster.","like_count":0,"author_name":"pierre chantelauze","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1367994"},{"created_at":"2013-01-10T22:49:07Z","content":"This is unnecessary and it needs to be put to an end","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alexis Johnston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7102169"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T14:59:14Z","content":"Car c'est cruel de faire souffrir les animaux et si je peux faire une petite diff\u00e9rence tout simplement en signant une p\u00e9tition,  je dois le faire. Merci.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lucie Lafrance","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36450845"},{"created_at":"2013-03-13T18:05:19Z","content":"i do not think that we have an ethiical resbonsibility and that no animal should suffer at the hand of a human.","like_count":0,"author_name":"gabriela deschamps","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/43930498"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T17:44:37Z","content":"Any animal abuse is abhorrent.  Pigs are extremely intelligent animals, more intelligent than your average dog.  I don't know how animal abusers sleep at 