cery store ever again!!!!! Second, to the CEO I do not believe a word you have said.  I think that you did know about the cruelty and kept quiet about it, I mean how could you not know?  You also said the majority of your workers are humane and kind to the animals , how can you say that?  If that were true they would have blown the whistle on the bastards that did this, so in my eyes and every one else's they are just as guilty as the ones committing the abuse.  You say that all the workers are trained on how to treat the animals, by whom, Jeffrey Dahmer? (Serial killer that started out abusing animals)  And even if all the employees were treating the animals with compassion the fact that they are being kept in those gestation crates is in itself one of the most inhumane things I have ever seen.  Also what kind of veterinarians do you employ?  Where did they get their degree, a cracker jack box?  Did they ever tour the facility, if they did they had blinders on because the shape of those poor animals is a disgrace.  Not only should the workers be fired and charged with animal cruelty, the veterinarians and management should be as well, the place shut down and burned to the ground.  I am absolutely infuriated and disgusted by what I have seen and by all involved in the abuse and the cover up!!!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Hilda Constantineau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/485257"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T09:11:25Z","content":"I read Charlottes Web when I was 10 years old.","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Carr","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36825266"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T04:17:43Z","content":"Just finished watching the youtube video provided by the \"Mercy for Animals\" organization on the Paratone farms in Manitoba...and I am ashamed and disgusted. \r\n\r\nNo animal should suffer this kind of treatment, ever. I am ashamed to say that I buy and eat meat. After seeing the type of conditions at the Paratone farm, I will either have to buy