ontent":"You do not have to be a vegetarian to hate what is happening to these animals who have the closest DNA match of all animals to humans. Boycott these stores!.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kevin McCormick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11558615"},{"created_at":"2013-01-03T19:40:02Z","content":"These stores have all lost a customer (and will continue to lose more as I share this information) until they choose to do something about this. This is terrible. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Best","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37907441"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T06:25:55Z","content":"Food animals deserve a quality of life that makes their lives worth living.  It is the least we can do for them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joshua Jarman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37059559"},{"created_at":"2012-12-23T18:02:45Z","content":"Mass production (GMO) of any animals is toxic when eaten by humans. \r\nWe should be grateful for what we have to consume in our lives and they should be given a natural healthy life before that time comes. This is incredibly cruel. If we each of us speaks up, we can make a change. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aivi Dam","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34956362"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T01:44:08Z","content":"I will be doing everything possible to spread the word about this horrible abuse, and make sure people stop giving any of these stores business!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kelly Anen-Nettesheim","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24499710"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:21:00Z","content":"I am so sick of animals being tortured for human consumption.  Human's have no heart or soul and have turned into the worst kind of animal.  I have no problem with eating an animal that was allowed to graze in a field and fed food that an animal should eat and not pumped with anitbiotics and hormones.  I'm sick of the way animals are abused.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rebecca Lipka","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23542176"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:49:07Z","content":"Disgusting business!  I hope that karma exists.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rosamund Downing","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/484884"},{"created_at":"2013-03-29T14:46:45Z","content":"This is the most repulsive thing I've ever heard. You'd have to have no morals to do this to another living thing.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emily Boocock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45651124"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T22:54:53Z","content":"Cette torture faite a ces pauvres animaux ...ca n a aucun sens, faut les prot\u00e9ger et meme arreter l \u00e9levage des porcs.....","like_count":0,"author_name":"sylvie sylvestre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16390240"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T21:04:12Z","content":"Animals don't deserve to suffer because of humans","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sofia Gonzales","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36474884"},{"created_at":"2013-02-02T05:56:46Z","content":"I believe we are all equal, no one person or animal deserves this treatment. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Vanessa Ford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9415597"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T00:59:11Z","content":"Because it's unacceptable to treat animals this way. They have feelings like us.","like_count":0,"author_name":"sarah verret","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36329319"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T22:21:53Z","content":"Chega, basta de crueldade com animais indefesos.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Del Conte Neusa","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8468375"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T23:47:23Z","content":"This kind of animal cruelty is disgusting and totally unnecessary. Regardless of whether or not people will continue eating pig products I find it totally incomprehensible that these companies feel the need to keep these animals in such poor conditions? How much difference would it make to treat them with a little dignity? It costs more to be cruel than to be kind.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dearbhla Crosse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2975453"},{"created_at":"2013-01-24T04:32:33Z","content":"This is sick! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Simone Dighton","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/39278395"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T21:37:20Z","content":"Human health, animal welfare and environmental sustainability are put at risk with this system - all of which I oppose vehemently.","like_count":0,"author_name":"kat inkster","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8955866"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T09:22:44Z","content":"Not only are animal voiceless in matters that affect them, but higher animals (biologically more elabobate ones) are 'aware' of their environment and tuned to what affects them, like severe pain and neglect. The degree of care (or lack thereof) that we allow ourselves to place upon them is a direct reflection of our advancement or regression, as a community. Showing complete disregard for animal life is a marker to the decline of our civilization and fragmentation of some of our most cherished values. When one producer/farmer allows willfully or unwittingly this type of behaviour towards animals, he/she tarnishes a whole industry, as if a malignant tumour was to find its way into our society. When this is brought to light, it also points to the authories' lack of thoroughness in dealing with such issue. The guilt is shared, it's great shame, but it is not unrepairable. new measures should be placed and offenders dealt with accordingly. I am glad I stumbled on this video and that someone took the courage to bring this out in the open. The industry just lost a customer with me.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Guillaume Peribere","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21295100"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T19:22:42Z","content":"Hard to believe this is happening in Canada...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sinead Archbold","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36386908"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T01:25:44Z","content":"We must speak for those that can't speak for themselves ...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Steve F","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26683489"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T02:42:57Z","content":"If you are what you eat, we're all quite tortured on the inside. The horrendous treatment of animals must stop. I will not buy food that has gone through these terrible conditions. Consider my comment a declaration of boycotting any company that continues to do this kind of inhumane treatment.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kirill Zaitsev","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25057215"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T03:05:50Z","content":"Every living being deserves to live humanely without torture before paying the ultimate price for human benefit.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ron Hildahl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12565415"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T03:40:05Z","content":"There are some things in this world that are just wrong. If we can't even stop to treat our own food with some dignity, then we have a serious problem.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephen Love","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25319310"},{"created_at":"2013-01-26T18:32:13Z","content":"Why is this allowed in Canada, for shame :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michele G.","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11264270"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T01:32:31Z","content":"\u201cThe greatness of a nation and its moral progress can be judged by the way its animals are treated\u201d Mahatma Gandhi","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Strul","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36414131"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T17:25:18Z","content":"This is important to me because I am compassionate about animals and would like to see a reduction in animal suffering.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Dustin Massop","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36840838"},{"created_at":"2012-12-29T04:37:29Z","content":"I am a non-vegetarian and like to consume meat. But I feel very bad the way the animals are treated. As a consumer I really can't accept that the meat I swallow into my mouth have to go through suck immense pain when they are alive as animals. I will stop buying if no serious action is being taken by the appropriate authority.","like_count":0,"author_name":"CHOONG WAIYUON","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37658222"},{"created_at":"2013-02-05T23:46:32Z","content":"The story of 46257 is shocking and unacceptable.  Reading about the treatement you'd think they where talking about the death camps of Nazi Germany rather than a factory farm.  This kind of cruelty is wrong and has to be stopped immedietly.  The factory farm that these poor pigs are from should be shut down and the horrible abuse and cruelty stopped.  As a Canadian the fact that this is allowed to happen in Canada greatly upsets me.  This cruelty has to stop now, and the people in charge of this factory farm should be made to answer for their crimes.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ben Stewart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34077266"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T02:01:31Z","content":"The abuse must stop.  Although there is no \"humane\" meat, they are still living beings that deserve to be treated with consideration.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Chris Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27213657"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T14:12:16Z","content":"These horrific conditions must be done away with. We're not some backwards third world country. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Evan Pretty","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22142438"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T16:41:10Z","content":"This act of torture is appalling. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Takaya Kerschbaumer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12376123"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:21:56Z","content":"Because i have a huge love for animals and especially pigs because they are always an animal that people just look at  as a meal.  They dont deserve this torture.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Laney Hopper","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16674939"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T21:17:40Z","content":"Life of all forms deserve respect. Peace.  ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stefan Haviland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/29988008"},{"created_at":"2013-01-06T23:45:06Z","content":"This is important to me because I believe non-human animals are as entitled to quality of life as humans   ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Daniela Battistella","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13106555"},{"created_at":"2013-01-04T18:22:11Z","content":"Because no animal deserves to be treated with such cruelty.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Mark van Dam","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37964038"},{"created_at":"2013-01-17T19:19:31Z","content":"Cause they are living creatures and should not suffer and be tortured...that is cruel. They should be able to walk around and have a wonderful life until their time comes.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maxine Gravel","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38835753"},{"created_at":"2013-01-02T16:18:39Z","content":"Healthy happy grass fed animals are the way to go!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jason Selby","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/17290787"},{"created_at":"2012-12-14T23:52:11Z","content":"Animals are God`s creatures too. They deserve to be treated with respect and compassion, and allowed to live as nature intended. Not brutalised and tortured by barbaric savages! They are living in HELL!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sadie Dempsey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/9975657"},{"created_at":"2013-01-11T16:20:55Z","content":"Stop animal cruelty!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Wade VanH","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26366430"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:08:30Z","content":"We have the power to be better, do better.  If we treat lesser beings this way, what are we showing our children, friends, family, the world - who we really are  :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bev Spencer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/6628451"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:47:44Z","content":"If people are going to continue eating meat, for their safety and human decency, we must demand humane practices in our food industry! I'm not sure why people have such a hard time empathizing -could you imagine being born and staying in one spot for years before you are expected top move to slaughter? ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Krista Krueger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13309213"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:55:13Z","content":"My heart is heavy today and a part of it will forever stay that way until the words \"gestation crates\" are only a memory. Please pay attention to this cause. These are lives hanging in our hands and if it only takes you a few clicks on your computer that you are probably on almost every day to save a life than what would anyone be waiting for. Imagine yourself in a cage not much bigger than your body for your ENTIRE LIFE! Feeling disturbed yet? Don't let 46257 die in vain. She has already had enough.\r\nSign the petition. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jess Mulholland","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28658594"},{"created_at":"2012-12-22T16:35:08Z","content":"I am appalled by these cruel practices I will no longer buy from stores that buy from farms that torture helpless animals. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Katherine Brock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31942391"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:38:43Z","content":"Slaughter houses torture and mistreat animals because they think nobody will find out or notice. Perhaps we should also be asking why it is that only sadistic people seem to be employed by slaughterhouses and breeding farms. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzanne Swan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35338028"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T07:42:46Z","content":"Because it is sick, sick, sick and inhumane! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joy Tougas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36500519"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:37:24Z","content":"Wel