e_count":0,"author_name":"Elizabeth Fey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16793360"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T15:47:48Z","content":"No animal should suffer. No one.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Am\u00e9lie Tourangeau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27089029"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:06:46Z","content":"because it effects the people around me that i love who may not be vegetarian. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marla Kasprick","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22919507"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:58:51Z","content":"Cruelty to animals should never be tolerated.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Madeline Blankenship","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11111875"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T14:22:45Z","content":"Pigs are smart animals.  They feel emotion and pain, have mental stress just as humans do. Metal gestation crates are torture cells.  Please have some compassion and see the need to stop using them.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cheryl Johnson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31066038"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T05:32:47Z","content":"Mental Stress etc. etc. etc to the animal and causing damage to the meat.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Rennie Urquhart","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37057872"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T17:25:23Z","content":"There is no need for this in our society. You don't have to be a vegetarian to demand that animals be accorded comfort and dignity before slaughter.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jeremy Sale","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21308708"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T02:01:38Z","content":"Animals have Rights too !!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Todd Sisunik","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36254805"},{"created_at":"2012-12-12T05:57:48Z","content":"I deeply care about the suffering caused to the livestock that is our food source.  I wish it would go away.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Matthew Block","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36426481"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T16:5