like_count":0,"author_name":"Anita Mar","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12407000"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T03:01:42Z","content":"We need to stop this insanity of torturing and killing animals that are as aware of pain and suffering as we are.  We wouldn't treat our dogs like this; why is it ok to treat pigs like this?","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robert Caine","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22858083"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T03:37:32Z","content":"It is our responsisbility to deal with all species with kindness, love and compassion.  That these intelligent pigs suffer through human cruelty is beyond understanding.  Please stop this madness.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Anne Robson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1185732"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T03:50:33Z","content":"Please sign and share The Department of Agriculture needs to be responsible and stop allowing these horrid conditions that farm animals are kept   The torture chambers for farm animals need to be ended now!  There is no excuse for the way people treat farm animals today.  The cruel and sick way farm animals are treated form the darkest chapter of history.  When people do not feel compassion for other living creatures, compassion drops greatly as it is today.  Anyone who has accustomed himself to regard the life of any living creature as worthless is in danger of arriving also at the idea of worthless human lives and is being proven today.  This factor Is being proven today.  This evolution of cruelty is spreading like a virus.   We must fight against the spirit of unconscious cruelty with which we treat the animals. Animals suffer as much as we do. True humanity does not allow us to impose such sufferings on them so those that work at these sick places are desensitized to the pain and suffering they are causing.  It is our duty to make the whole world recognize it. Until we extend our circle of compassion to all living things, humanity will not find peace. \r\n\r\nAnimals have a God Given Right to be here and not to abuse, torture, and kill.  And Jesus did say unto them, Verily I say unto you, they who partake of benefits which are gotten by wronging one of God\u2019s creatures, cannot be righteous; nor can they touch holy things, or teach the mysteries of the kingdom. It ill becomes us to invoke in our daily prayers the blessings of God, the Compassionate, if we in turn will not practice elementary compassion towards our fellow creatures\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Susan Pateracki","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8224381"},{"created_at":"2013-04-12T13:02:02Z","content":"Reading the story of 46257 broke my heart. She suffered a miserable life and wasn't even allowed a merciful death. So many more pigs continue to suffer like her day after day! We must end this cruelty!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melinda Elliott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13582791"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:52:55Z","content":"all life has value and should be treated with more respect.  These animals have personalities and feelings and deserve better.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erin Langford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37017938"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:48:37Z","content":"Its a brutal torture on animals ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Upasana Singh","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7045794"},{"created_at":"2013-02-10T03:02:34Z","content":"Because animals are living creatures with feelings just like us. They have the right to a decent life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marie-Eve Laspeyres","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41092080"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:15:24Z","content":"I am a meat eater. I do not deny nor feel ashamed for it. However I do my best to eat animals that are treated well and allowed to grow freely. I pay more for this choice but it is the only choice possible for me. In reality, there chould be no choice. All animals should be treated in an ethical fashion","like_count":0,"author_name"