illed to feed people, it is completely unnecessary to torture them beforehand.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brian Otto","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23643566"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:01:44Z","content":"Animals are totally feeling creatures, we should honor and respect what they give to us, not be cruel...we are the stupid ones then.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynette Pelley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25311242"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T04:24:01Z","content":"It sickens me that pigs are tortured by big cooperations all in the name of the all mighty dollar.  I never gave a second thought to buying my neatly wrapped grocery packed pork.  Who naive was I too assume that pigs raised for slaughter were not humanely treated from birth to death.  I assumed they were raised on some Aunt Sally's type farm barn. Being birth and weened by their mothers , the freedom of movement to forage in the mud and socialize with other pigs to do the natural thing piggies do.  Since watching the w5 segment I have been in a deep depression as what I witnessed was nothing short of an atrocity all at the hands of humans.  The bar on the treatment of pigs raised for slaughter from birth to death has to be raised now!!!  We Ned companies to be advocates and promote and advertise the ethical treatment of pigs so that other cooperations will follow","like_count":0,"author_name":"Crystal Riediger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36340646"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:41:08Z","content":"We need to treat the animals that we raise as food with respect.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Potts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35941355"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T21:52:21Z","content":"No animal should be caged in this manner or treated with such cruelty.  They cannot speak for or defend themselves.  Hopefully, this petition will be the voice that they need.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pat Romanko","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35968028"},{"creat