count":0,"author_name":"Christie Stein","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5843309"},{"created_at":"2013-01-19T03:50:14Z","content":"Meat is Murder","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sarah Alcocer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1881246"},{"created_at":"2012-12-29T21:51:01Z","content":"No being deserves to suffer this way","like_count":0,"author_name":"Emma Fletcher","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16877793"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:56:01Z","content":"I'm a conscious consumer. this is animal cuelty","like_count":0,"author_name":"trasi henen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36305341"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:40:16Z","content":"I love pigs.  They are very smart, and this cruelty is disgraceful.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Carol Riley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24137396"},{"created_at":"2013-01-04T17:11:44Z","content":"Many pigs are treated this way everyday. It is horrible the way That pig factory farmers treat these animals. They don't eat natural foods either. The farmers want to use the least amount of money possible. They don't think about what is best for the animal. They resort sometimes to feeding the pigs manure or waste, other dead pig carcases or pig meat. They pump the pigs with antibiotics and hormones so they will grow faster and produce more meat. And when we eat these pigs, we are digesting the hormones, antibiotics and waste that the pigs ate, which is unhealthy for us too.  farmers don't care how they treat the animals. They treat them as if they aren't living, as if they are inanimate objects. How would we feel lying in a cage on a cement floor, in dark room unable to see sunlight or even move? Imagine that for just a day. Well, that is how these pigs live. Except they live in that kind of environment for a lifetime. They don't ever get to live like normal animals. They don't even get to be outside. They don't get to run, they don't even get to move. The farmers of these pigs know how cruel they are treating them. But it means getting more meat, which is more money. I strongly believe\r\nin putting a stop to this kind of torture. The least we can do is to buy only pork that we know has been treated well and not support companies that torture the animals. We can help put a stop to it, and get grocery chains to stop supporting these companies. We can put an end to gestation crates, and pigs can live happier lives.\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"K M","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35047491"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T23:14:45Z","content":"This is absolutely disgusting, barbaric,cruel and sick. Stop this IMMEDIATELY!!!!!!!!!! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynn Reece","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2616508"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T02:43:55Z","content":"Why are humans so cruel :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Aaron Saunders","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36334445"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:31:01Z","content":"This life is not a life it resembles more of an experimental scientific cloned pig, being fed experimental scientific foods (IDNW) and the less they move, the faster they get plump and ready for consumption by humans.  We are what we eat with an epidemic of cancer.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Salvati","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32181454"},{"created_at":"2013-01-22T05:01:06Z","content":"It is your moral obligation to ensure that animals do not suffer in life and at moment of death.  Have the decency to start treating these poor souls with respect or get ready to lose money as others like my family and friends will refuse to eat pork!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"marica czirfusz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2299253"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:04:35Z","content":"I am an animal lover and even though I eat meat, an animals life still has value and deserve to be happy n comfortable up to the end.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sheri Gibson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36143111"},{"created_at":"2