y to have peace in this world. We must be vegan. World Vegan, World Peace.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jean Campbell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26488681"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T15:38:01Z","content":"Please be kind to animal.","like_count":0,"author_name":"grace landa","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/7954269"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T14:25:07Z","content":"We owe all sentient creatures a decent life and death. Shame, shame, shame...","like_count":0,"author_name":"E and E MAY","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36286490"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T15:06:45Z","content":"STOP this ATROCIOUS, CRUEL and UNNECESSARY TORTURE NOW!!!! BOYCOTT UNTIL THIS STOPS!!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maria Aguirre","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/16895286"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T10:26:32Z","content":"I raise pigs outside and I can't imagine them being imprisoned in crates.  They are individuals with awareness about their world.  People have to say no to this cruelty.  Rights are obtained through struggle.  We must give the voiceless a LOUD voice.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ruth Pryzner","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/35620003"},{"created_at":"2012-12-24T12:33:30Z","content":"I agree with the following: J.F.\r\nI dislike the thought that some animal has been made miserable to feed me. If I am going to eat meat, I want it to be from an animal that has lived a pleasant, uncrowded life outdoors, on bountiful pasture, with good water nearby and trees for shade.\u201d \r\n\u2015 Wendell Berry, What are People For?","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Fefchak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37288772"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T16:48:07Z","content":"Animals provide us with nourishment - physically, mentally and emotionally.  We need to be respectful and thank them by being kind to them esp, before they are slaughtered for food for us humans.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenny Seow","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36295994"},{"cr