941916"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T04:53:12Z","content":"I'm not surprised \"Darrel\" from Mercy for Animals is haunted for life from working undercover at the gestation crate factory pig farm in Manitoba. Employed by an animal rights group, Darrel was required to act normal, do what he was told, and participate, if necessary, in killing animals. It seems like Darrel may be haunted because there was that little space in his brain that told him he could blow it all in seconds, if he broke the agreement he had with Mercy for Animals ... if only perhaps he had just grabbed that individual pig, 46257, put her on a front loader, loaded her into the back of his car, and taken her to an emergency animal hospital, he would have been fired from the factory farm he was investigating and as well, fired from Mercy for Animals. I can see why he is haunted. This farm was so horrific that Darrel will now have nightmares for the rest of his life, and will always wonder what the outcome would have been had he followed his heart and not his paycheck and his principle, just like all the other employees do at the factory pig farm in Manitoba, and made a difference in that poor, defenseless pig's life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Sorvino","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/801715"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T21:25:07Z","content":"Life is important.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jonathan Tang","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36115436"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T21:34:23Z","content":"All animals deserve humanity ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erin Andrews","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37037530"},{"created_at":"2012-12-09T14:22:39Z","content":"Animals desserve our respect.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nicole  brien","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/12802556"},{"created_at":"2012-12-21T00:22:14Z","content":"it's just wromg","like_count":0,"author_name":"Robert Wozney","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32709452"},{"created_at":"2012-12-13T20:53:25Z","c