 them to die, that too should happen very quickly and with as much dignity and as little violence as is possible.  At this point in time I still believe in the \"food chain\" as long as all animals have a LIFE until it is their time to go.  But I have to say that ever since I first became aware of the conditions often present in factory farming, I have been more careful where I buy my meat, and having a difficult time finding \"good places,\" I have considered going vegetarian more then ever.  That any animal should live in such horror breaks my heart, makes me sick, and even makes me ashamed to be of the human species:'(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda Klics","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11137069"},{"created_at":"2013-03-05T22:07:30Z","content":"I feel so very pety for all those pigs, who suffer extremely - also in my country. Look into the eyes of the animal and see the pain. We have no right to treat animals like this. But we have the duty to take care and protect all animals from cruelty.Charity include also animals.\r\nWith kindly regards\r\nInge Winther","like_count":0,"author_name":"Inge Winther","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32971865"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:05:23Z","content":"I love meat; we must show animals kindness and humanity for the food they give us.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bruce LePage","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27792689"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:31:02Z","content":"I worked at a store with it's very own barn and slaughter house. Although the animals weren't kept in small, confined cages the conditions were no better. There were animals bleeding and cut, animals who were sick, animals who have been injured, and animals who have died while in those pens we had. I've seen animals barely walk up those ramps. The conditions that these animals lived in were absurd and inhumane. Despite cleaning those pens in my honest opinion; I still deemed them unclean.\r\n\r\nThis needs to stop. A farm animal may have it's fate to be eaten; this is something we all now. However; if we claim to kill our animals \"humanly\".. why can't we treat them \"humanly\" even to the last possible moment? This petition is the start to something great. This petition is the start to humane treatment towards the animals from life to death. Good meat is happy meat; that's an old farmers saying that's been for years. We cannot allow \"demand\" to be the reason these animals are packed up in tight area's, force fed, and left bleeding, bruised, and dead. It's time for change.\r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Denis Lovrincevic","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37019917"},{"created_at":"2013-01-11T19:25:11Z","content":"this is completly unacceptable.  if  all canadians knew how these animals were being treated there would be outrage.  It's too bad it falls under the media radar of important things to talk about","like_count":0,"author_name":"arlene duggan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/38432734"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:14:35Z","content":"It really is cruel","like_count":0,"author_name":"Victor Rafuse","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/37032197"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T16:42:25Z","content":"we as humans have to start being more humane to our animals....they are living breathing creatures with feelings and brains","like_count":0,"author_name":"donald bennetts","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36374126"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T20:56:33Z","content":"anyone in their right mind would not tolerate knowing how these pigs are treated ----  i want this to stop RIGHT NOW and will do anything in my power to make this stop --- please everyone sign and do the right thing ","like_count":0,"author_name":"carol messer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21856181"},{"created_at":"2012-12-28T18:04:12Z","content":"animal cruelty is disgusting","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jenna  Watt","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/jennawatt11"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T18:24:28Z","co