n","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28967435"},{"created_at":"2013-04-30T03:52:21Z","content":"This is just sickening practice to condone by selling products produced by such barbaric companies. They are not even human. Cut them off! ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Bronwyn Burles","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25762477"},{"created_at":"2013-04-01T20:27:08Z","content":"So sad :(","like_count":0,"author_name":"Suzanne Davidson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/45873672"},{"created_at":"2012-12-27T03:36:34Z","content":"If I eat an animal I hope its life has been one that I would be glad to share.","like_count":0,"author_name":"William Roff","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3533276"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T17:26:58Z","content":"this is a moral issue, as well as a health issue and an environmental issue. For all these reasons, this is clearly and majorly wrong. It needs to stop. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Wearne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/8858477"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T18:05:27Z","content":"All living beings need to be treated humanely.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pat Petro","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/22918595"},{"created_at":"2012-12-10T19:07:10Z","content":"STOP THE CRUELTY! JUST STOP EATING MEAT. IT IS SO EASY","like_count":0,"author_name":"bonnie mcewan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/499272"},{"created_at":"2012-12-25T21:10:08Z","content":"I would like to see theses so-called farmers locked up in their own livestock crates for several days or better yet - weeks. Shame on them. There are significantly better places to buy groceries than Loblaws etc. \r\nGood luck in your most worthwhile petition. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Paula Jongerden","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/31397374"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T00:01:58Z","content":"Animals should not have to go through this agony. As Canadians we should work for a country with the fair treatment of all, including animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cornelia Hordijk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/26941744"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:07:04Z","content":"My Canada does not allow inhumane treatment, of human or animal. It's time to evolve, as a people and a Country. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adrienne Calvert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/adriennecalvert"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:12:41Z","content":"Sobey's has done great work by becoming the best grocery chain on sourcing sustainably-caught seafood. I expect that Sobey's and Loblaws will  demonstrate their commitment to ensuring the food that ends up on our plates does no harm. Metro and Walmart are committed to the cheapest, so I think they'll be making the assumption that people don't care. People would care if they didn't feel overwhelmed with their inability to change things simply for the caring about it. They are fatigued and expect decision makers to have some point on which they won't compromise - and price doesn't cut it.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jane Sorensen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2439010"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T15:32:21Z","content":"This is disgusting. I will not shop at Sobeys, Walmart, Metro or Loblaws/Superstore anymore. What a horrible life these poor creatures have. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Audrey Hoddinott","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21394040"},{"created_at":"2012-12-11T08:40:17Z","content":"Because we have no rights to act this way. Period.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Stephane Farrese","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36347710"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:26:22Z","content":"pigs are intelligent creatures who should not be treated so inhumanely.","like_count":0,"author_name":"stephanie dudley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32842327"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T16:32:03Z","content":"Animals, even if born just for suppling food, should also have a happy and healthy life before they go to their grave. This is just unacceptable.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erica Rios","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36107808"},{"created_at":"2012-12-15T06:26:54Z","content":"There is no need to torture living beings before killing them in order to supply us with meat. Even someone who doesn't really care about animal rights, surely cannot be against allowing them to live and die pain-free.","like_count":0,"author_name":"francine janura","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25410769"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:22:12Z","content":"Animals being raised for food need to be \"animals\" during their lifetime. (Grass fed beef, free range chickens, etc).\r\nI completely disagree with factory farming.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kay Calvin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/15589688"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:41:13Z","content":"Kill pigs humanely, this is terrible. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Keilan Faganello","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25002099"},{"created_at":"2012-12-18T00:00:33Z","content":"Humane treatment of meat animals is one of the most important ways to maintain high quality meat.\r\nEthical treatment issue not, the better the quality of life of the animal, the better the food product you get from it.\r\nAfter learning about how pigs were treated, I switched to Tamworth pork and Berkshire pork.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Struan Robertson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/36792045"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T17:59:47Z","content":"I love animals.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Douglas Shearer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/14573619"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T18:07:07Z","content":"Animals should be treated with respect and dignity.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jen Houston","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/546267"},{"created_at":"2012-12-20T19:07:26Z","content":"We have a responsibility to ensure the best husbandry possible!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Jordan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/34901106"},{"created_at":"2012-12-19T18:29:06Z","conten